NK067(ju)001:1: // dri sh+te n+aa r+tha bu d+d+ha na mo gu h+ya
NK067(ju)001:2: ga r+b+ha s+ya sa m+aa ny+aa r+tha bi ha ra
NK067(ju)001:5: // gsang ba snying po'i spyi don mthong bas don rtogs zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK067(ju)001:7: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK067(ju)001:8: pa'i spyi don gyi ngag bgros gu ru lugs su
NK067(ju)001:9: bkod pa mthong bas don rtogs zhes bya ba dpal
NK067(ju)001:10: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK067(ju)001:11: dbyings rig zung du 'jug pa rig pa'i gshis //
NK067(ju)001:12: mi 'gyur don dam 'pho med rtag pa'i dngos //
NK067(ju)001:13: 'dus ma byas pa mkha' khyab mkha'i rdo rje //
NK067(ju)001:14: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying por phyag bagyi'o //
NK067(ju)001:15: 'gyur med sems kyi gnas lugs mngon 'gyur phyir //
NK067(ju)001:16: bskyed rdzogs gshog rlabs bskyod pa'i rnam 'phrul gyis //
NK067(ju)001:17: thabs grol mkha' las rdo rje'i sar bkri ba //
NK067(ju)001:18: thabs rgyud lam gyi snying por dang bas 'dud //
NK067(ju)001:19: rang snang ris med mi 'gyur sku gsum rdzogs //
NK067(ju)001:20: gzhom med lhan cig skyes pa bde ba'i dngos //
NK067(ju)001:21: rdo rje sems mchog dpal ldan 'khor lo'i mgon //
NK067(ju)001:22: 'bras rgyud de bzhin gshegs la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK067(ju)001:23: shin tu rtogs dka' zab gsang snying po'i don //
NK067(ju)001:24: ngag tshig brjod pas 'doms la dbang 'byor bas //
NK067(ju)001:25: chos kun zab gnad ston pa'i byed pa po //
NK067(ju)001:26: dpal ldan rdo rje 'dzin mchog rgyal gyur cig /
NK067(ju)001:27: mchog tu gsang ba brtan g.yo'i dngos kun gshis //
NK067(ju)001:28: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs bcud snying po'i don //
NK067(ju)001:29: 'khrul med de bzhin nyid du ston byed rgyud //
NK067(ju)001:30: nges pa'i zab gnad don kun 'dir gsal bya //
NK067(ju)001:31: de la 'dir gang bshad bya'i chos ni /
NK067(ju)001:32: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i
NK067(ju)001:33: rgyud dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK067(ju)001:34: nges pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid
NK067(ju)001:35: yin la / de gang gis 'chad na /
NK067(ju)001:36: lung rigs man ngag gsum gyis 'chad de /
NK067(ju)001:37: de la lung gis ji ltar 'chad ce na /
NK067(ju)001:38: grol lam rim cig car du ston pa rdo rje me long dang /
NK067(ju)001:40: thabs lam rim cig car du ston pa rgya mtsho dang thal ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:41: de ltar bshad rgyud sde bzhi sogs rgyud rnam par dag pa rnams kyis so //
NK067(ju)001:42: man ngag gis ji ltar 'chad na /
NK067(ju)001:43: 'phags yul gyi pan grub chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK067(ju)001:44: bi ma la mi tra sogs spyi dang /
NK067(ju)001:45: khyad par sgeg rdor gyi rgyas 'grel spar khab dang /
NK067(ju)001:46: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sgyu 'phrul lam rim sogs la brten nas 'chad /
NK067(ju)001:47: bod kyi mkhas pa chen po so zur gnubs gsum /
NK067(ju)001:48: khyad par zur mes dbon rnam gsum sogs kyis bstan bcos rnam dag la brten nas so //
NK067(ju)001:49: rigs pas ji ltar 'chad ce na /
NK067(ju)001:50: lung man ngag dang mi 'gal ba'i rigs pa rnam par dag pas so //
NK067(ju)001:52: sgeg rdor gyi rgyud gsum snang ba bzhir bsdus nas gsung /
NK067(ju)001:53: zur chung shes rab grags kyis chos lngar bsdu ba
NK067(ju)001:54: sogs 'chad tshul gyi bka' srol du ma yod kyang
NK067(ju)001:55: / 'dir bi ma la'i rjes su 'brangs te 'chad na /
NK067(ju)001:57: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK067(ju)001:60: 'go smos pas go ba'i dbang po yang rab rnams la mtshan bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:61: dbang po 'bring po rnams la spyi'i don rnam par dbye bas bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:62: dbang po tha ma rnams la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas spros te bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)001:63: skabs 'dir sa bcad dang po gnyis ston te /
NK067(ju)001:64: de la dang po 'go smos pas go ba'i dbang po yang rab rnams la mtshan bshad pa la'ang /
NK067(ju)001:66: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK067(ju)001:67: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK067(ju)001:68: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK067(ju)001:69: skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:71: rab la mtshan bstan pa de la'ang tha snyad gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:72: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa rgyud dang mthun pa'i mtshan /
NK067(ju)001:73: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa zhes pa man ngag dang mthun pa'i mtshan /
NK067(ju)001:74: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi zhes pa lung dang mthun pa'i mtshan te /
NK067(ju)001:75: gtso che ba'i dbang du mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags shing /
NK067(ju)001:77: sman pas lag gi rtsa bltas pas lus mgo mjug gi nad shes pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:78: de la mtshan gyi rnam grangs gsum las /
NK067(ju)001:79: dang po rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang
NK067(ju)001:80: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsum gyi mtshan thun mong du
NK067(ju)001:81: bstan pa ni / rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:82: de la mtshan gyi zur gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:83: dang po rdo rje sems dpa' ni /
NK067(ju)001:85: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:86: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK067(ju)001:87: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK067(ju)001:88: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:91: rdo rje stong pa nyid du brjod //
NK067(ju)001:92: sems dpa' ye shes tsam nyid de //
NK067(ju)001:93: de dag bdag nyid grub pa ni //
NK067(ju)001:94: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes brjod do //
NK067(ju)001:95: zhes pas rdo rje ni shes rab stong pa nyid do //
NK067(ju)001:96: stong pa nyid de la tshur mtshan ma'i chos gang
NK067(ju)001:97: gis kyang mi phyed cing phar mtshan chos thams cad
NK067(ju)001:98: 'joms nus pas rdo rje dang chos mtshungs pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:99: de ltar btags / sems dpa' ni /
NK067(ju)001:100: sa t+wa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK067(ju)001:101: spyir sat+wa don drug la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)001:102: snying stobs te zhe sdang dang /
NK067(ju)001:107: bsdus pa rnams la 'jug pa las /
NK067(ju)001:108: skabs 'dir brtan bsdus rtogs gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:110: sems can kun gyi sems gang ni //
NK067(ju)001:111: rdo rje zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:112: brtan pa'i phyir na sems dpar brjod //
NK067(ju)001:115: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pas na //
NK067(ju)001:117: mi phyed rdo rje zhes brjod do //
NK067(ju)001:118: sems dpa' srid gsum gcig pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:119: 'di na shes rab ldan pa yis //
NK067(ju)001:120: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes su bshad //
NK067(ju)001:123: skye med ye shes rang gi dbyings //
NK067(ju)001:124: mi 'gyur mi shigs rdo rje'i don //
NK067(ju)001:125: sems dpa' ye shes rdo rje ste //
NK067(ju)001:126: zhes pas yul can thabs rang rig pa byang chub
NK067(ju)001:127: kyi sems yul shes rab dbyings stong pa nyid dang
NK067(ju)001:128: ro gcig pa'i zung 'jug rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK067(ju)001:129: dag pa de ni rdo rje ltar brtan pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:130: brtan pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ste mchog
NK067(ju)001:131: tu mi 'gyur ba'i cha nas bzhag /
NK067(ju)001:132: zung 'jug de'i phyag rgyas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK067(ju)001:133: cad la btab pas 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par
NK067(ju)001:134: mnyam pa nyid du bsdus pa ni bsdus pa'i rdo
NK067(ju)001:135: rje sems dpa' ste rnam kun mchog ldan gyi cha
NK067(ju)001:136: nas bzhag cing / de ltar brtan bsdus gnyis po de gnas lugs kyi ngos nas bzhag ste /
NK067(ju)001:137: de'i phyir gnyis po de la gzhi 'bras gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:138: de lta bu'i gnas lugs kyi don gdod ma nas
NK067(ju)001:139: rang chas su bzhugs pa de nyid sgrib gnyis zad
NK067(ju)001:140: cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyes bus rang gi rang
NK067(ju)001:141: bzhin ji lta ba bzhin mngon du rtogs pa ni
NK067(ju)001:142: 'bras bu'i rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK067(ju)001:143: snang lugs kyi ngos nas bzhag la /
NK067(ju)001:144: gang rtogs pa'i ye shes de yang rdo rje ltar
NK067(ju)001:145: gnyis su med par gyur pa'i phyir de skad ces
NK067(ju)001:146: bya'o // de nyid mtshon byed mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar snang ba dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang /
NK067(ju)001:147: skabs 'dir thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang du byas
NK067(ju)001:148: te 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje mi bskyod pa
NK067(ju)001:149: la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:150: de la dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo ni /
NK067(ju)001:151: las dang po pas don spyi'i tshul du bsgoms pa brtags pa'i lha sku /
NK067(ju)001:152: 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim grub pa'i sa mtshams sbyor lam
NK067(ju)001:153: gyi dus su rlung sems kyi lha sku rang shar
NK067(ju)001:154: / mthong lam 'od gsal gyi lha sku //
NK067(ju)001:155: slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku ste lam gyis bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang /
NK067(ju)001:156: mi slob pa'i zung 'jug 'og min du bzhugs pa'i
NK067(ju)001:157: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK067(ju)001:158: rnams so // mtshan gyi zur gnyis sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:160: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK067(ju)001:161: zhes pas sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'ang thabs shes zung 'jug gi don te /
NK067(ju)001:162: de la dang po rtog tshogs sgyu d+r+wa ni /
NK067(ju)001:165: snang ba ris su ma chad pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:168: rgyu 'byung ba'i ris su ma chad pa'i rgyus 'bras
NK067(ju)001:169: bu phung po lngar 'phrul pa'i phyir rgyu 'bras gnyis
NK067(ju)001:172: de gnyis rgyu 'bras 'brel pa can gyi sgo zung du 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:173: gnyis pa nges don sgyu d+r+wa ni /
NK067(ju)001:174: shes rab dbyings stong pa nyid chos can /
NK067(ju)001:176: ris med kun khyab kyi chos nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:177: thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chos dang /
NK067(ju)001:179: stong nyid kyi rtsal snang rig pa rang byung gi ye shes su ma 'gags par 'phrul pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:182: stong nyid kyi rtsal snang ye shes su 'char la
NK067(ju)001:183: ye shes kyi rang bzhin stong par grol ba'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:184: / gsum pa drang don brda'i sgyu d+r+wa ni /
NK067(ju)001:185: gang du drang na nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la /
NK067(ju)001:186: gang drang na mtshan ma'i blo can rnams /
NK067(ju)001:187: ji ltar drang na sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum /
NK067(ju)001:189: d+r+wa ba mtshon pa yab yum zhal sbyor gyi brdas so //
NK067(ju)001:190: bzhi pa lha rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu d+r+wa ni /
NK067(ju)001:191: rtog tshogs ni sgyu ma ste /
NK067(ju)001:192: snang la rang bzhin ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:194: rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rtsal snang lhar snang ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:195: d+r+wa ba ni rang bzhin gnyis su med par 'brel ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:196: rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin lha yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:199: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes la //
NK067(ju)001:200: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK067(ju)001:204: mang la 'brel ba d+r+wa ba'i don //
NK067(ju)001:206: 'di nyid kyi le'u bzhi pa las ni yab la sgyu 'phrul dang /
NK067(ju)001:207: yum la d+r+wa bar bshad de /
NK067(ju)001:208: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK067(ju)001:210: tha ni d+r+wa ba brtan pa nyid //
NK067(ju)001:212: de ltar gzhi dang 'bras bu'i zung 'jug la mtshan
NK067(ju)001:213: ji skad du thob pa'i nges pas las kyi rgyud
NK067(ju)001:214: de la'ang de skad ces bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:215: gzhi 'bras gnyis dang shes thob kyi bya byed 'grel pa can du gnas pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:216: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud sgrar snang zhing sgrar grags pa'i rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)001:217: brdar btags glegs bam gyi rnam par bkod pa 'di
NK067(ju)001:218: la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes
NK067(ju)001:219: bya'o // gnyis pa che ba las mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:222: so so bstan pa rgya tsho'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)001:224: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK067(ju)001:225: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:227: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis
NK067(ju)001:228: gdul bya so so'i blo dang 'tshams par bstan pa'i
NK067(ju)001:229: theg pa'i rnam grangs ni zab cing rgya che bas
NK067(ju)001:230: rgya mtsho'i rgyud ces bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:231: de lta bu'i bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad
NK067(ju)001:232: kyi don 'di'i nang du ston pas 'dir ston zhes
NK067(ju)001:233: bya ste / bshad rgyud rgyas pa las /
NK067(ju)001:234: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK067(ju)001:235: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK067(ju)001:236: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK067(ju)001:237: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK067(ju)001:239: bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad rgyud 'dis rdzogs par ston pas 'dis ston zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:241: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK067(ju)001:245: bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad kyang 'di nyid
NK067(ju)001:246: rtogs pa'i thabs su ston pas 'di phyir ston zhes
NK067(ju)001:247: bya ste / sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK067(ju)001:248: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK067(ju)001:250: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir theg pa thams cad kyi don
NK067(ju)001:251: rgyud 'di la yongs su rdzogs pas lung gi spyi
NK067(ju)001:252: zhes bshad la / de yang gsang ba spyi rgyud
NK067(ju)001:253: lta bu min par bstan pa dang theg pa thams
NK067(ju)001:254: cad kyi lung gi spyi yin no zhes 'chad par
NK067(ju)001:255: zhes bshad la / byed pa la / mtshan nyid
NK067(ju)001:256: dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi zhes pa'i
NK067(ju)001:258: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa'i
NK067(ju)001:259: mtshan glegs bam gyi klad du bkod dgos tshul ni
NK067(ju)001:261: sngon du 'gro ba'i bdag nyid pas //
NK067(ju)001:262: ming nyid thog mar smos pa gces //
NK067(ju)001:263: zhes pas glegs bam gyi klad du bkod pa'i mtshan te /
NK067(ju)001:264: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:266: gsang ba ni gzhi rgyud rtogs dka' ba /
NK067(ju)001:267: snying po ni lam gyi rgyud de bstan pa thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa /
NK067(ju)001:268: de kho na nyid ni gzhi mi 'gyur ba dang lam gyis de rtogs pa la mi bslu ba /
NK067(ju)001:269: nges pa ni sgro skur dang bral bar gtan la phab pa'i don te /
NK067(ju)001:271: gsang ba chos 'byung la bshad de //
NK067(ju)001:272: snying po'ang de yi thabs can no //
NK067(ju)001:273: gnyis pa phyin ci ma log phyir //
NK067(ju)001:274: de nyid do 'dir rnam nges so //
NK067(ju)001:277: gzhi rgyud de bzhin nyid de rtogs dka' zhing kun gyi snying por bzhugs pas gsang ba'i snying po /
NK067(ju)001:278: lam rgyud ni gzhi rtogs pa dang 'bras bu thob pa la mi bslu bas de kho na nyid /
NK067(ju)001:279: 'bras bu'i rgyud ni sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK067(ju)001:280: 'khor du nges pa'o zhes bshad kyang rung ste rdo
NK067(ju)001:282: gnyis pa dbang po 'bring po rnams la spyi'i don rnam par dbye bas 'chad pa la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)001:283: don gyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:284: tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:288: 'bras bu yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud don /
NK067(ju)001:290: 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:291: dang po la ngo bo ni /
NK067(ju)001:293: ston pa la sogs rab dbye bas //
NK067(ju)001:294: phun sum tshogs pa lngar brjod do //
NK067(ju)001:296: gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa de la /
NK067(ju)001:297: ston pa dang la sogs pas /
NK067(ju)001:301: dus phun sum tshogs pa ste lngar brjod la /
NK067(ju)001:305: 'khor gang dang lhan cig tshogs pa de'i tshe rgyud
NK067(ju)001:306: don 'byung bar nges pa'i phyir phun sum tshogs pa
NK067(ju)001:309: ci'i phyir gleng gzhi zhes bya zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:311: d+aa na'i sgra las drangs na sbyin pa zhes pa la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)001:312: gang la na bka' yin min du rtog pa'i the tshom can dag la sbyin /
NK067(ju)001:314: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i lo rgyus brjod pas so //
NK067(ju)001:316: yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin no //
NK067(ju)001:317: 'on kyang bod skad du sbyin pa zhes bsgyur na
NK067(ju)001:318: dngos po sbyin pa lta bu phyogs gcig tu chad
NK067(ju)001:319: 'gro bas bod kyi brda dang sbyar te lo ts+aa
NK067(ju)001:320: ba rnams kyis gleng gzhi zhes bsgyur ba'i dbang du
NK067(ju)001:321: / gang gleng bar bya ba rgyud kyi don 'byung ba'i rgyu'am gzhir gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:322: dbye na thun mong min pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)001:323: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:325: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud rgya mtshos bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:326: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:330: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK067(ju)001:331: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK067(ju)001:332: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK067(ju)001:333: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK067(ju)001:334: ye shes myong bas bsdus par bshad //
NK067(ju)001:335: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK067(ju)001:336: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK067(ju)001:337: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK067(ju)001:338: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK067(ju)001:340: gnas phun sum tshogs pa snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo //
NK067(ju)001:341: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa srog mi shigs pa'i thig le /
NK067(ju)001:342: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rnam shes tshogs brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:343: chos phun sum tshogs pa don dam 'od gsal la nam mkha'i gzugs can /
NK067(ju)001:344: dus phun sum tshogs pa dus gsum mnyam nyid do //
NK067(ju)001:347: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK067(ju)001:348: e sogs rnam bzhi dbyibs can gnas //
NK067(ju)001:349: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK067(ju)001:350: wam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:351: ma d+aa ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK067(ju)001:352: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK067(ju)001:353: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK067(ju)001:354: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)001:355: ya na theg chen 'di yin no //
NK067(ju)001:356: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK067(ju)001:357: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:359: gnas phun sum tshogs pa yum gyi mkha' gsang /
NK067(ju)001:360: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa yab kyi rdo rje kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems dang bcas pa /
NK067(ju)001:361: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa byed pa sdom pa'i thabs dang bcas pa'i gsang ba'i rnam shes /
NK067(ju)001:362: chos phun sum tshogs pa rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:363: dus phun sum tshogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK067(ju)001:364: 'di dag gleng gzhir 'gyur ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:365: rgyun mtha'i sa la bzhugs pa'i lhan cig pa'i 'khor
NK067(ju)001:366: rnams la ston pas 'bras dus kyi dbang bskur bas
NK067(ju)001:367: nang gi mngon byang lnga la brten nas yang dag
NK067(ju)001:368: pa'i mtha' mngon du mdzad pa de ston 'khor dgongs
NK067(ju)001:369: pa dbyer med du gyur pa'i dus der snying ga
NK067(ju)001:370: dang gsang ba'i 'og min du mngon par rdzogs par
NK067(ju)001:371: 'tshang rgya ba'i rgyu mtshan gyis nang gsang gnyis gleng
NK067(ju)001:373: de'i phyir thun mong min pa'i gleng gzhi zhes kyang bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:374: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng gzhi la gsum las /
NK067(ju)001:375: dang po longs sku'i gleng gazhi'am rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi la /
NK067(ju)001:376: chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:377: 'di skad bshad pa zhes pas bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:378: 'di skad ces pa tshig 'phrad de rgyud don rdzogs bar 'chad pa'i don no //
NK067(ju)001:379: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:380: dus na zhes pa rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo'o //
NK067(ju)001:381: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK067(ju)001:385: de bzhin gshegs yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK067(ju)001:386: bcom ldan 'das longs spyod chen po zhes sogs kyis
NK067(ju)001:387: bstan te / spyir ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun du 'du zhing /
NK067(ju)001:388: de yang rigs bsdu na bzhir 'du ste /
NK067(ju)001:390: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK067(ju)001:391: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK067(ju)001:392: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK067(ju)001:393: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:396: phyag rgya bca' ba'i sgo nas dang /
NK067(ju)001:397: bsgyur ba'i sgo nas las bya ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:398: dang po ni dpal he ru ka'i las bzhi'i phyag rgya bca' ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:400: yan lag snying po rtse gcig dang //
NK067(ju)001:403: chos dbyings don gyi 'og min dang /
NK067(ju)001:406: gtsang ris kyi lha lnga'i nang tshan 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min rnams las /
NK067(ju)001:407: 'dir ni 'og min chen po bya ba longs spyod rdzogs sku'i zhing khams te /
NK067(ju)001:409: gtsang ma'i ris dag rnam spangs pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:410: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK067(ju)001:414: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa na //
NK067(ju)001:415: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK067(ju)001:416: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang //
NK067(ju)001:419: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la zhes pas bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:420: de dag gi don bsdu na /
NK067(ju)001:422: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK067(ju)001:423: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK067(ju)001:424: rgyan dang sgo khyud rta babs dang //
NK067(ju)001:425: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK067(ju)001:428: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)001:429: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:432: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK067(ju)001:438: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:439: sogs kyis nang sems yab yum dang /
NK067(ju)001:440: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed dang /
NK067(ju)001:441: sogs kyis phyi sems yab yum bstan /
NK067(ju)001:443: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg pa dang sogs kyis bstan /
NK067(ju)001:444: gzhan yang rgyud mas sbyangs kyi tshogs dpag tu med
NK067(ju)001:445: pa dang lhan cig bzhugs so zhes ston pa la
NK067(ju)001:446: / de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyi mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK067(ju)001:448: zhar byung dogs pa bsal ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:449: le'u dang po nas bshad pa'i longs sku'i gleng gzhi
NK067(ju)001:450: 'di nyid sangs rgyas rang snang dang gdul bya gzhan
NK067(ju)001:452: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na
NK067(ju)001:453: zhes sogs gzhung dngos bstan ltar yin lugs nas rang
NK067(ju)001:454: snang gi gleng gzhi yin mod /
NK067(ju)001:455: 'on kyang gdul bya la ltos nas gzhan snang gi gleng gzhi yin pa'ang mi 'gal te /
NK067(ju)001:456: gleng bslang gi dus su rgyun mtha'i byang sems la
NK067(ju)001:457: 'bras dbang bskur nas gnas der 'tshang rgya bar bstan
NK067(ju)001:458: pas rgyun mtha'i sems dpa' de dag ston 'khor dgongs
NK067(ju)001:459: pa dbyer med du ma 'gyur gong du gdul bya
NK067(ju)001:460: de'i blo ngor gzhan snang gi gleng gzhi snang ba
NK067(ju)001:463: dang po sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK067(ju)001:464: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK067(ju)001:465: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK067(ju)001:466: rnam gnyis tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:468: gnyis pa zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi la /
NK067(ju)001:469: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:470: bzod par dka' ba'i dur khrod chen po ste /
NK067(ju)001:471: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas sogs kyis bstan /
NK067(ju)001:472: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:473: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal he ru ka ste /
NK067(ju)001:474: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sogs kyis bstan /
NK067(ju)001:476: gdul bya gdug pa can gyi 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)001:479: ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:480: de la ru drar gol tshul dang /
NK067(ju)001:481: gol ba'i 'bras bu smin tshul lo //
NK067(ju)001:484: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang sogs kyis ma
NK067(ju)001:485: rig pa'i rgyus sems can thams cad spyir 'khrul tshul
NK067(ju)001:486: bstan nas / bye brag ru dra rang gi gol tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:487: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas /
NK067(ju)001:489: sngon bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su byung ba'i dge slong thar pa nag po lta bu ste /
NK067(ju)001:490: gol gzhi thub dka' gzhon nus /
NK067(ju)001:491: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK067(ju)001:492: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK067(ju)001:493: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK067(ju)001:495: zhes gsungs pa la sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas gol ba bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:497: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs nas sogs kyis
NK067(ju)001:498: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu dmyal ba dang yi dwags
NK067(ju)001:500: de nas las kyi sgrib pa rtsub mo'i rnam par
NK067(ju)001:501: smin pa de sogs kyis rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu
NK067(ju)001:502: ru drar skyes tshul dngos bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:503: gnyis pa 'dul byed gnyen po'i 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:504: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te sogs kyis rigs bzhi yab yum /
NK067(ju)001:505: dkar mo'i tshogs dang sogs kyi gnas ma brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:506: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang sogs kyis yul ma brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:507: rdo rje sring 'gro ma'i tshogs dang sogs kyis gdong mo bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:508: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang sogs kyis dbang mo nyer brgyad rnams bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:509: skabs 'dir spyir dbang mo rnams gdul bya'i 'khor yin
NK067(ju)001:510: kyang ngo mtshar tshogs kyi sras mo rnams bskyed pa'i
NK067(ju)001:511: yum yin pas 'dul byed du bsdus so //
NK067(ju)001:512: chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:513: thabs lam sbyor sgrol gyi thabs rmad du byung ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:517: de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu dang gsum gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:518: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK067(ju)001:520: ming gi dbang bskur te dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du bkod do //
NK067(ju)001:521: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:522: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:523: de'i dus su 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa kun tu sogs kyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:525: khro bo'i gleng gzhi 'di la zhar byung zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK067(ju)001:526: rgyun mtha'i sems dpa' rnams la ston pas 'bras dbang
NK067(ju)001:527: bskur ba'i dus der nang du snang gsum gyi sgrib
NK067(ju)001:528: pa bcom pa'i brdar phyi rol du ru dra 'khor
NK067(ju)001:529: dang bcas pa'i snang ngor khro bo'i gleng gzhi snang
NK067(ju)001:530: ba'i phyir de skad ces smos la /
NK067(ju)001:531: gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa'i don /
NK067(ju)001:532: sngon byung du gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:533: ma 'ongs pa'i gdul bya dbang rnon brtul zhugs can
NK067(ju)001:534: rnams gsang sngags kyi nye lam sbyor sgrol gyi thabs
NK067(ju)001:535: khyad par can la bkri ba'i ched yin cing /
NK067(ju)001:536: khyad par rdzogs rim gyi dus su skyon can gyi
NK067(ju)001:537: rtsa dang las kyi rlung thig gi rgyu ba bcom
NK067(ju)001:538: nas ye shes kyi rtsa rlung thig ler sbyor ba'i
NK067(ju)001:539: gnad khyad par can ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:540: gsum pa sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gazhi'am /
NK067(ju)001:541: bstan pa spyi'i gleng gzhir grags pa la /
NK067(ju)001:542: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:543: spyir gtso che ba'i dbang du byas nas /
NK067(ju)001:544: phyogs bzhi steng 'og dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten drug gam /
NK067(ju)001:545: yang na yas kyi 'jig rten lha mi 'phred bstan gyi 'gro ba dud 'gro ste s+n+rel gzhi /
NK067(ju)001:546: mas kyi 'jig rten yi dwags dang dmyal ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:547: mdor na de dag gis bsdus pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po gcig ste /
NK067(ju)001:548: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi
NK067(ju)001:549: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi
NK067(ju)001:552: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:553: 'jig rten gyi khams stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK067(ju)001:554: re rer mchog gi sprul sku re re don mdzad
NK067(ju)001:555: cing de yang 'jig rten drug gam /
NK067(ju)001:556: gdul bya rigs drug la ltos nas thub pa drug ste /
NK067(ju)001:557: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK067(ju)001:559: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)001:563: lha mi sogs theg pa lnga'i ris can gyi gdul bya lnga'am /
NK067(ju)001:564: 'gro 'dul thub pa drug la ltos nas lha min
NK067(ju)001:565: stod ris lha dang smad ris dud 'gror bsdus pa'i
NK067(ju)001:566: rgyud lnga'o // chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:569: sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba /
NK067(ju)001:571: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK067(ju)001:572: gsung rig pas 'dul ba dang bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:573: gsung rig pas 'dul ba de la /
NK067(ju)001:574: theg pa lngar phye bas mdor bstan /
NK067(ju)001:575: chos phung brgyad khri bzhi stong du dbye bas rgyas par bshad /
NK067(ju)001:576: de yang dbang po'i bye brag gis lngar bsdu ba dang gsum gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:579: gos su med par ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK067(ju)001:580: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:581: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:582: sgron ma bkod pa'i dus zhes bya ba sangs rgyas
NK067(ju)001:583: mchog gi sprul sku 'jig rten du byon pa'i dus
NK067(ju)001:584: te / shin tu dkon pa'i dus na'o //
NK067(ju)001:587: sngar bshad le'u bco lnga pa khro bo'i gleng gzhir ma zad /
NK067(ju)001:588: le'u gsum pa'i gleng gzhi 'di yang le'u dang po'i gleng gzhi'i zhar byung du 'gro ste /
NK067(ju)001:589: longs sku dngos kyi gdul zhing du ma gyur pa'i
NK067(ju)001:590: go phye ba'i 'khor rnams la 'di'i lam stegs kyi
NK067(ju)001:591: theg pa spyi dang khyad par rgyud 'di sogs rang
NK067(ju)001:592: rang gi dbang po dang 'tshams par chos ston pa'i
NK067(ju)001:593: phyir / ston pa longs sku las ma g.yos bzhin
NK067(ju)001:594: du gang 'dul gyi sprul skur snang nas don mdzad
NK067(ju)001:596: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK067(ju)001:599: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK067(ju)001:601: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la /
NK067(ju)001:607: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK067(ju)001:608: skabs las gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK067(ju)001:609: gnang 'dri'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK067(ju)001:610: de des gsung la ma reg pa //
NK067(ju)001:611: zhes pa ston 'khor dri lan gyi sbyor bas rgyud
NK067(ju)001:612: don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par 'byung ma rag
NK067(ju)001:613: pa ste / de yang 'jam dpal mtshan brjod lta bu 'khor gyis zhus pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:614: mdo sdud pa lta bu ston pas mdun bsus pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:616: nges tshig ni ci'i phyir gleng bslang zhes bya zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:617: gang gleng bar bya ba ni rgyud don yin la /
NK067(ju)001:618: de nyid gleng bar bskul ba ni bslang ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:619: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:620: dbye na thun mong min pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)001:621: thun mong gi gleng bslang gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:623: lhan cig pa'i 'khor la gsang dbang bskur ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:624: dbang gong ma gnyis lhan cig tu bskur ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:626: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po /
NK067(ju)001:627: zhes sogs kyis thabs shes la sbyor tshul dang /
NK067(ju)001:628: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mos /
NK067(ju)001:629: zhes sogs kyis shes rab thabs su rol tshul bstan /
NK067(ju)001:630: de ltar ston pa yab yum gnyis su med par mnyam par sbyar ba las /
NK067(ju)001:631: rgyu yab yum gyi byang chub kyi sems dang rkyen de'i tshe /
NK067(ju)001:633: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK067(ju)001:634: zhes sogs yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung nas rtog
NK067(ju)001:635: tshogs thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du dag tshul
NK067(ju)001:636: gyis gleng bslang bas 'khor rnams kyi rgyud la lhag
NK067(ju)001:637: pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa rtogs par byas /
NK067(ju)001:639: phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK067(ju)001:640: zhes sogs yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung nas
NK067(ju)001:641: dngos po bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad chos nyid
NK067(ju)001:642: skye ba med pa'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pa'o zhes
NK067(ju)001:643: gleng bslang bas 'khor rnams kyi rgyud la don dam
NK067(ju)001:644: rtog med kyi ye shes mngon du byas mod /
NK067(ju)001:645: 'on kyang ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ye
NK067(ju)001:646: shes chen po da dung ma myong ba'i phyir spyod
NK067(ju)001:647: yul min pas gsang ba'i dbang zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:648: gnyis pa la dbang gnyis kyi sngon 'gro thun mong ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:649: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK067(ju)001:650: zhes sogs mtshar dang po bzhis bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:651: de la 'khor gyi rgyun mtha'i sems dpa' rnams rang
NK067(ju)001:652: snang ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang snyoms par zhugs
NK067(ju)001:653: pa'i thabs kyis rtsa gnas nas thig le g.yos te
NK067(ju)001:654: bde ba 'go ldang ba'i tshul du skyes pa g.yo
NK067(ju)001:656: bde ba phyi ma 'jug pa'i tshe snga ma 'jig
NK067(ju)001:657: cing mthar thams cad 'gag pa 'byin 'jug byang chub
NK067(ju)001:658: kyi sems / rten can gyi bde ba rang sa
NK067(ju)001:659: na gnas pa'i tshul gyis thams cad gnas pa gnas
NK067(ju)001:661: snga ma'i bde bas mtshon nas phyi ma'i bde ba
NK067(ju)001:662: la dmigs shing 'dun pa smon pa byang chub kyi
NK067(ju)001:663: sems te / de dag ni dbang gnyis kyi sngon 'agro'o //
NK067(ju)001:665: e ma'o sogs mtshar lnga'i tha mas bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:666: nyi zla byang chub kyi sems yas babs 'gro ba'i
NK067(ju)001:667: sbyor bas rdo rje dang pad+ma'i sna rtser zhal mjal
NK067(ju)001:668: ba las thabs shes rab tu sbyor ba /
NK067(ju)001:669: shes rab thabs su sbyor ba /
NK067(ju)001:670: thabs shes gnyis med du sbyor ba gsum gyi sgo
NK067(ju)001:671: nas dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams
NK067(ju)001:672: su myong ste shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob
NK067(ju)001:673: nas don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes rgyud la
NK067(ju)001:674: skyes pa'o // de nyid slar ldog pa'i thabs kyis
NK067(ju)001:675: rang gnas su 'ong bas mas brtan gyi dga' ba
NK067(ju)001:676: bcu drug gi mthar dkar dmar gyi cha steng 'og
NK067(ju)001:677: tu thim pa'i skad cig gnyis par rlung yang 'gags
NK067(ju)001:678: pas de gsum gyi 'gyur ba myong ba'i shes rig
NK067(ju)001:679: kyang rgyud chad de bde ba chen po'i dbang thob
NK067(ju)001:680: nas lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don ji
NK067(ju)001:681: lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur te ston 'khor dgongs
NK067(ju)001:682: pa dbyer med du gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:683: sngon byung gi dbang gsum po 'di ma 'ongs go
NK067(ju)001:684: phye ba'i 'khor la ltos na rgyud 'byung ba'i gleng
NK067(ju)001:686: 'on kyang lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams kho na la ltos nas gleng bslang ba /
NK067(ju)001:688: rgyud don rtogs pa gsum ngo bo gcig la ldog pa so sor snang ba tsam yin no //
NK067(ju)001:689: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng bslang ni /
NK067(ju)001:690: 'khor rnams kyi gzhan don du gsang ba bzhis chod
NK067(ju)001:691: pa rnams la thugs rjes bzung bar rigs zhes gsol
NK067(ju)001:692: ba btab pa las ston pa'i thugs rje skyes te
NK067(ju)001:693: rgyud 'dis dngos su 'dul ba'i yul du gyur pa
NK067(ju)001:695: gdul bya thun mong ba rnams la rgyud nas bstan
NK067(ju)001:696: par bya ba'i phyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprul
NK067(ju)001:697: sku thub pa drug spro ba sogs thugs rje chen
NK067(ju)001:698: po rol pa rnam pa sna tshogs ston par mdzad
NK067(ju)001:699: de / de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK067(ju)001:700: btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas ched du brjod pa
NK067(ju)001:701: de / 'di brjod do // zhes pa nas /
NK067(ju)001:702: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK067(ju)001:703: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:704: gsum pa 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)001:705: brjod bya gtso che ba'i dbang du rgyud gsum gyi rnam bzhag spyir bshad /
NK067(ju)001:706: rjod byed gtso che ba'i dbang du lam gyi cha
NK067(ju)001:707: rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bye brag tu bshad pa'o
NK067(ju)001:710: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK067(ju)001:712: zhes pas spyir rgyun chags pa'i don gyis na rgyud ches bya la /
NK067(ju)001:714: gang rtogs par bya ba gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)001:715: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)001:716: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud do //
NK067(ju)001:718: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:719: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK067(ju)001:722: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK067(ju)001:723: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK067(ju)001:725: gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang rig pa
NK067(ju)001:726: byang chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med spyod yul
NK067(ju)001:727: dang bral bar ye nas gnas pa gang yin pa
NK067(ju)001:728: ste de la rgyu rgyud ces bya la /
NK067(ju)001:730: rgyu rgyud de rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor
NK067(ju)001:731: 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gyur bas
NK067(ju)001:733: de nyid gnas lugs la 'ching grol thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:734: rgyu mtshan 'ching byed 'khrul ba'i chos med snang glo bur ba yin pas bcings pa med la /
NK067(ju)001:735: bcings pa med na grol ba mi 'byung ba chos
NK067(ju)001:736: nyid yin pa'i phyir 'ching grol med pa ces bya
NK067(ju)001:737: zhing / sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po
NK067(ju)001:738: de gsar byung min par gdod ma nas yongs grub
NK067(ju)001:739: rtag pa 'dus ma byas kyi rang bzhin du bzhugs
NK067(ju)001:741: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:742: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems su 'du la /
NK067(ju)001:743: de yang rang rig byang chub sems kyi ngo bor 'dus pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis de ltar du btags /
NK067(ju)001:744: bden pa dbyer med ces pa'i don /
NK067(ju)001:745: dbyings spros ba thams cad dang bral ba'i cha nas rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)001:746: rang gsal sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i cha nas ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:747: de las sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te
NK067(ju)001:748: 'bras chos lnga 'char rung ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun
NK067(ju)001:749: gyis grub pa'i cha nas 'bras bu don dam ste
NK067(ju)001:750: de ltar dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis
NK067(ju)001:751: grub pa lhag pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:752: de'i rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)001:753: dkyil 'khor rab 'byams su 'char ba lhag pa kun
NK067(ju)001:755: de gnyis ngo bo dbyer med zung 'jug yin pas na bden pa dbyer med ces bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:756: de la bden pa gnyis zung du 'jug tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:757: gcig gis gcig mi gtong ba'i zung 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)001:758: gser dang gser gyi ser po'am /
NK067(ju)001:759: mar me dang mar me'i 'od bzhin du don dam
NK067(ju)001:760: gyi snang ldog kun rdzob tu rang shar ba'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:761: / de ni bsam brjod kyi yul thams cad las
NK067(ju)001:762: 'das pas spyod yul dang bral ba zhes btags shing
NK067(ju)001:763: / / de nyid brtan g.yo 'khor 'das kyis bsdus
NK067(ju)001:764: pa'i chos thams cad la khyab chas su ye gdod
NK067(ju)001:765: ma nas gnas pa gang yin pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:766: khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang /
NK067(ju)001:767: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs dang /
NK067(ju)001:769: dri bcas de bzhin nyid la sogs pa'i tha snyad gang la 'jug pa'i gazhi'o //
NK067(ju)001:770: de dag gi don bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:771: chos kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dbyings sam khams /
NK067(ju)001:772: dri ma dang 'brel yang rang gi ngo bo sangs rgyas yin pas bde gshegs snying po'o //
NK067(ju)001:773: sems nyid stong cha nas chos sku dang snang cha
NK067(ju)001:774: nas gzugs sku'i yon tan rdzogs par ldan yang dri
NK067(ju)001:775: ma ma dag par rang gi bya ba byed mi
NK067(ju)001:776: nus pas rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs so //
NK067(ju)001:777: rang gi ngo bo rang byung gi ye shes yin
NK067(ju)001:778: la rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor 'das kun
NK067(ju)001:779: gyi 'char gzhir gyur pas kun gzhi'i ye shes so
NK067(ju)001:780: // chos nyid de bzhin de snang lugs la dri
NK067(ju)001:781: ma'i sbubs kyis bcings par snang bas dri bcas de
NK067(ju)001:783: sogs khong nas kri yas bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK067(ju)001:784: u pa yas byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)001:785: yo gas thog mtha' med pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK067(ju)001:786: sam byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po dang
NK067(ju)001:787: / ma h+aa yo gas byang chub kyi sems dbyer
NK067(ju)001:788: med spyod yul dang bral ba'am bden pa dbyer med
NK067(ju)001:789: lhag pa'i chos sku chen po /
NK067(ju)001:790: a nus dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK067(ju)001:791: sras bde ba chen po rtsa ba byang chub sems
NK067(ju)001:792: kyi dkyil 'khor / a tis 'od gsal byang chub
NK067(ju)001:793: kyi sems stong gsal 'gag pa med pa'i gnas lugs
NK067(ju)001:794: ye shes gsum ldan la sogs pa ming du mar
NK067(ju)001:795: kyi dkyil 'khor / grags so // rgyu rgyud de
NK067(ju)001:796: nyid gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi ldog cha gang rung
NK067(ju)001:797: dang ma bstun par spyir bzhag pa na rang bzhin
NK067(ju)001:798: nam gnas lugs zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:799: gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i zung 'jug rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'o //
NK067(ju)001:800: ldog cha so sor phye ste glo bur gyi dri ma sbyong ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:801: dri ma de nyid lam rgyud kyis bsal zhing sbyangs
NK067(ju)001:802: pa'i stobs kyis 'bras bu ji lta ba bzhin mngon
NK067(ju)001:803: du gyur pa la ltos nas lam dang 'bras bur
NK067(ju)001:804: bzhag go // ci'i phyir gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:805: thabs lam gyi rkyen gyis zin pa las myang 'das
NK067(ju)001:806: dang ma zin pa las 'khor bar 'grub par byed
NK067(ju)001:807: pas na / 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i 'byung gazhi'am rgyur gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)001:808: de nyid sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du
NK067(ju)001:809: rang bzhin 'gyur ba med par rgyun chags su 'jug
NK067(ju)001:812: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK067(ju)001:813: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK067(ju)001:816: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK067(ju)001:817: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK067(ju)001:822: dang po rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK067(ju)001:823: ngo bo'i gzhi dang btags pa'i gzhi //
NK067(ju)001:825: sems chos nyid gdod ma nas rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK067(ju)001:826: par dag pa rgyu rgyud bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK067(ju)001:827: po ni skabs 'dir sbyang gzhi ste dri ma sbyong
NK067(ju)001:830: 'dam rdzab kyi dbus kyi yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)001:831: de la ni gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:832: gzhi mtshan nyid pa yin no //
NK067(ju)001:833: log pa'i zhen snang yul dang bcas pa ni sbyang bya'i dri ma 'dam rdzab lta bu ste /
NK067(ju)001:834: med snang glo bur ba yin pas 'khrul ba btas pa'i gzhi zhes gsungs so //
NK067(ju)001:836: gnyis med la gnyis su 'dzin pa'i log pa'i zhen snang ste /
NK067(ju)001:837: de las las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'i 'khrul ba'i yul dang bcas pa'i rigs gnas so //
NK067(ju)001:838: zhen snang nyid 'khor ba 'grub byed kyi rgyu dang /
NK067(ju)001:839: rnam shes kyi 'jug pa ma zad bar rgyun chags
NK067(ju)001:840: pa tsam yin pas rgyu rgyud kyi ming tsam thogs
NK067(ju)001:841: kyang skabs 'di'i rgyu rgyud min te /
NK067(ju)001:842: bcos ma glo bur gyi chos yin pas 'bras bu'i
NK067(ju)001:843: nyer len du gyur pa'i rgyu rgyud min pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:844: / rigs pas dpyad don gyi ston nyid ces bya ba ka ba ka ba'i chos nyid dang /
NK067(ju)001:845: bum pa bum pa'i chos nyid kyis stong pa lta
NK067(ju)001:846: bu med dgag gi stong nyid kyang skabs 'dir rgyu
NK067(ju)001:847: rgyud mtshan nyid pa min te /
NK067(ju)001:848: nyer len gyi rgyu dang rgyun gyi don gnyis ka mi gnas pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)001:849: med dgag de nyid spros bral tsam yin kyang 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i rgyu min la /
NK067(ju)001:850: 'dus ma byas pa tsam las rgyun gyi don yang ma tshang ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:851: 'on kyang rgyu rgyud btags pa bar bzhag pa la 'gal ba med de /
NK067(ju)001:852: de la dmigs na skyon yon skye ba dang gnas
NK067(ju)001:853: skabs rig ngor rgyun chags pa tsam yin pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:854: / gnyis pa gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud ni /
NK067(ju)001:855: rgyu rgyud bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po de glo
NK067(ju)001:856: bur gyi dri ma dang bral bar byed pa'i thabs
NK067(ju)001:857: te / de yang dang por thos bsam gyis lta
NK067(ju)001:858: ba'i gnas lugs don spyi'i tshul du shes par byas
NK067(ju)001:859: te / nas / de ltar shes pa'i don la
NK067(ju)001:860: nyams su len pa'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i byed rtsol
NK067(ju)001:862: de yang ngo bo skyed byed thos bsam sgom pa'i
NK067(ju)001:863: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis bskyed bya thun mong
NK067(ju)001:864: dang / mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam skye ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:865: de ltar yang rim gsum las /
NK067(ju)001:866: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK067(ju)001:867: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:869: skabs 'di'i thun mong gi sems lnga ni /
NK067(ju)001:874: phyi rgyud sde gsum ste thun mong gi lam lnga dang mthun pa'i sems lnga yin la /
NK067(ju)001:876: ma h+aa yo ga ba rang lugs kyi sems lnga ste /
NK067(ju)001:877: sems lnga po gang zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:878: lam la 'jug 'dod kyi sems dang por 'go ldang ba g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)001:879: de thob na ci ma rung snyam pa smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)001:880: de la 'jug pa 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)001:881: zhugs nas gnas pa gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)001:882: de don mthar phyin pa mthar phyin byang chub kyi sems so //
NK067(ju)001:883: sems lnga po de dag gi skye tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:885: gzhi dang skabs nas skye 'gyur ba //
NK067(ju)001:886: grol thar lam du rnam par bshad //
NK067(ju)001:887: ces pas gzhi nas sems bskyed pa /
NK067(ju)001:891: mun pa'i sa nas sems bskyed pa zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:892: lam ma zhugs kyi gang zag zhig thog ma nas lam 'di la zhugs te /
NK067(ju)001:893: rang 'bras mthar phyin par byed pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:895: lam stegs kyi theg pa gang rung zhig la zhugs
NK067(ju)001:896: nas slob bzhin pa las khyad par gyi lam 'di
NK067(ju)001:899: lam stegs kyi theg pa gang yin yang rung /
NK067(ju)001:900: rang lam gyi mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du
NK067(ju)001:901: byas nas slar nye lam rmad du byung ba'i lam
NK067(ju)001:903: zhar byung de dag gi dogs sel ni /
NK067(ju)001:904: lam dang 'bras bu'i sa nas sems bskyed pa gang yin kyang rung /
NK067(ju)001:905: nyan rang man chad rang lam gyi mi slob lam
NK067(ju)001:906: mthar phyin par bsgrubs kyang theg chen gyi tshogs lam
NK067(ju)001:908: byang sems yan chad lam dang 'bras bu gang nas
NK067(ju)001:909: zhugs kyang mo tshod mthun pa'i sa nas zhugs pas
NK067(ju)001:911: ci'i phyir thabs sam lam gyi rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:912: thob bya 'bras rgyud nyid mngon du byed pa'i lhan cig byed rkyen yin pas thabs dang /
NK067(ju)001:913: gang gis gang du bgrod bya'i rten yin pas lam ste /
NK067(ju)001:914: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK067(ju)001:915: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK067(ju)001:916: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK067(ju)001:917: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK067(ju)001:919: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:921: lam de la'ang nye ring gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:922: rnal 'byor bla na med pa khyad par gyi lam 'di ni nye ba'i lam mam /
NK067(ju)001:924: lam 'di mthar phyin par bsgrubs nas lam gzhan gyi bsnon ma mi dgos pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:925: de las gzhan pa thun mong gi lam ni /
NK067(ju)001:926: ngan song las nges pas 'byung ba lha mi /
NK067(ju)001:927: 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba nyan rang /
NK067(ju)001:928: mtha' gnyis la nges par 'byung ba byang sems te nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)001:929: phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi lam rnams ni skabs 'dir ring ba'i lam zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:930: rang lam gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin nas kyang 'di la 'jug dgos pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:931: lam de ni gzhi shes par byed pa la mar 'brel /
NK067(ju)001:932: 'bras bu thob par byed pa la yar 'brel bas
NK067(ju)001:933: shes thob kyi bya byed dang 'brel ba'i thabs bar
NK067(ju)001:934: ma chad pas rgyud du bzhag go //
NK067(ju)001:935: khyad par gyi lam la dbye na /
NK067(ju)001:936: thabs kyi nges pa'i lam dang /
NK067(ju)001:937: shes rab rnam par grol ba'i lam gnyis te /
NK067(ju)001:939: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK067(ju)001:942: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK067(ju)001:943: zhes pas gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par brtul zhugs
NK067(ju)001:944: kyi spyod pa rmad du byung ba'i sgo nas 'bras
NK067(ju)001:945: bu myur du 'grub par byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:946: lam thabs grol gnyis phan tshun ltos pa can yin
NK067(ju)001:947: pas gtso che ba'i dbang du byas te gtso bor
NK067(ju)001:948: zhes smos la / spyir thabs zhes bya ba lam
NK067(ju)001:949: thams cad la 'jug kyang 'dir thabs mkhas kyis zin
NK067(ju)001:950: ma zin gyi khe nyen che bas spyi ming bye
NK067(ju)001:951: brag la sbyar te thabs kyi khyad par zhes bya
NK067(ju)001:952: zhes smos la / zhing / 'di lta bu'i spyod
NK067(ju)001:953: tshul khyad par can de ni gang zag brtul zhugs
NK067(ju)001:954: dang ldan pa kho na'i spyod yul yin pas de
NK067(ju)001:955: zhes smos la / zhing / ltar grags la /
NK067(ju)001:956: rmad du byung ba zhes pa ya sha ba'i don
NK067(ju)001:957: zhes smos la / zhing / ltar grags la /
NK067(ju)001:958: te / 'ching byed kyi las la spyod pa ltar
NK067(ju)001:959: gnang bas grol ba 'di 'dra ngo mtshar zhing ngam
NK067(ju)001:960: zhes smos la / zhing / ltar grags la /
NK067(ju)001:961: te / pa'o // des ni 'bras bu phyi dus
NK067(ju)001:962: su mi lus par myur du 'grub par byed pa
NK067(ju)001:963: zhes smos la / zhing / ltar grags la /
NK067(ju)001:964: te / pa'o // ste / dpe mak+shi ka bya
NK067(ju)001:965: ba dngul chu las bsgrub pa'i gser 'gyur gyi rtsi
NK067(ju)001:966: zhes smos la / zhing / ltar grags la /
NK067(ju)001:967: te / pa'o // ste / ste / des lcags
NK067(ju)001:968: gser du bsgyur ba'i tshe rtsi de nyid kyis lcags
NK067(ju)001:969: la btab ste thabs dang ldan pas bsregs pa na
NK067(ju)001:970: gnas skabs lngas gser du bsgyur ba bzhin te /
NK067(ju)001:971: de la gnas skabs lnga ni /
NK067(ju)001:972: du ba dang ni rtseg rtseg dang //
NK067(ju)001:973: sbal pa 'chong ba nyid dang ni //
NK067(ju)001:975: dngul chu yi ni gnas skabs lnga //
NK067(ju)001:977: myur bar ma zad kha nyen che ba'i dper yang 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)001:978: bsreg pa'i thabs la mkhas na lcags gser du 'gyur ba la dka' tshegs med cing /
NK067(ju)001:979: thabs dang mi ldan na me nyid dngul chu'i dgra
NK067(ju)001:980: yin pas lcags gser du mi 'gyur bar ma zad
NK067(ju)001:981: rtsi de yang 'thor te chud zos su 'gro ba
NK067(ju)001:984: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK067(ju)001:985: zhes pa ltar gnyis las dang po steng sgo ni /
NK067(ju)001:986: 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor
NK067(ju)001:987: bas 'khor lo bzhir bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa
NK067(ju)001:988: la bslab pa rim gyis pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:990: lus kyi lte bar rtsa gsum 'khor lo drug dang bcas pa gsal btab /
NK067(ju)001:991: de la rtsa gsum ni lus kyi dbus rtsa dbu ma /
NK067(ju)001:993: g.yon du rkyang ma gsum gyi dbu ma tshangs bug nas gsang gnas kyi bar drang thal le ba /
NK067(ju)001:994: ro rkyang gnyis rtse mo gug ste yar sna bug gnyis su zug pa /
NK067(ju)001:995: mar sna gsang gnas dang bshang sgor zug pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:996: dbu ma'i mar sna lte 'og sor bzhi man chad
NK067(ju)001:997: dbu ma dang rtsa rgyud gcig kyang las tha dad
NK067(ju)001:998: pa'i phyir dung can ma zhes bya la /
NK067(ju)001:1000: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum cu so gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:1001: mgrin par longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug /
NK067(ju)001:1002: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:1003: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi ste rtsa ba'i 'khor lo bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:1004: de 'og sor bzhi gzhal ba na me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum thig le ram gyis mtshan pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1005: de 'og sor bzhi gzhal ba rgyu zhabs kyi thad
NK067(ju)001:1006: du rlung gi dkyil 'khor gzhu'i dbyibs can yam gyis
NK067(ju)001:1007: mtshan pa ste rkyen gyi 'khor lo gnyis rnams gsal
NK067(ju)001:1008: btab nas / rlung bum pa can sbyor ba bzhi
NK067(ju)001:1009: ldan la sogs pa'i thabs dang ldan pas nyams su
NK067(ju)001:1010: btab nas / blangs pa las / bshad kha'i rlung g.yos /
NK067(ju)001:1012: 'khor lo bzhi'i gnas rgyud de dbu ma'i yar rtser
NK067(ju)001:1013: ham yig bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin mgo bo
NK067(ju)001:1014: thur bstan gyi tshul du gnas pa la reg pas
NK067(ju)001:1015: bdud rtsi byang chub kyi sems babs pa spyi bo
NK067(ju)001:1016: nas mgrin par sleb pas dga' ba /
NK067(ju)001:1017: mgrin pa nas snying gar sleb bas mchog dga' //
NK067(ju)001:1018: snying ga nas lte bar sleb pas khyad dga' /
NK067(ju)001:1019: lte ba nas gsang par lhan skyes kyi dga' ba
NK067(ju)001:1020: nyams su myong ste slar yang mas brtan gyis bsdus
NK067(ju)001:1021: pa'i dga' bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong ba las
NK067(ju)001:1022: mthar bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)001:1023: khyad par can rgyud la skyes pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1024: de skad du yang rgya mtsho las /
NK067(ju)001:1025: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK067(ju)001:1026: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK067(ju)001:1027: bzho bas steng du rnam bar grags //
NK067(ju)001:1029: de dag ni steng sgo thun mong ba yin la /
NK067(ju)001:1030: khyad par ba ni 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gsum par bshad pa ltar te /
NK067(ju)001:1035: khyab brdal chen po'i man ngag go //
NK067(ju)001:1037: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK067(ju)001:1038: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad yod pa bzhir bsdus ste /
NK067(ju)001:1039: mdun chos nyid kyi rtsa gsum /
NK067(ju)001:1040: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa gcig /
NK067(ju)001:1041: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa gcig /
NK067(ju)001:1042: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:1043: rtsa de dag gi sbubs na 'od bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)001:1044: de'i khrod na sbyang bya sbyong byed kyi sa bon rnam shes dang bcas pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1045: de dag gi dbus na dwangs ma lnga la brten
NK067(ju)001:1046: pa'i ye shes snying po'i thig le stong gsal 'gag
NK067(ju)001:1047: med bde ba chen po'i ngo bo bzhugs pa la
NK067(ju)001:1048: / spyi bo nas mar sems gtad de bsgoms pas
NK067(ju)001:1049: de nyid 'od du 'bar bas sbyong byed kyi sa
NK067(ju)001:1051: des rigs drug gi sa bon gnyid dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK067(ju)001:1052: rags rlung thams cad dwangs ma la thim pas rnam
NK067(ju)001:1053: rtog thams cad mi rtog pa'i klong du thim zhing
NK067(ju)001:1054: dmigs med mtha' bral bde ba chen por byang chub
NK067(ju)001:1056: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK067(ju)001:1057: lte ba'i rtsa 'dab kyi dbus na dbyings phyug lnga'i
NK067(ju)001:1058: thig le a thung gi rnam par gnas pa la
NK067(ju)001:1059: / snying ga nas mar sems gtad pas snying ga'i
NK067(ju)001:1060: thig le'i bde drod mar song ba lte ba'i thig
NK067(ju)001:1061: / le la phog / de nyid 'od du 'bar zhing rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su gsal /
NK067(ju)001:1062: de'i drod slar yang yar song ste snying ga'i dwangs
NK067(ju)001:1063: ma la thim pas dwangs ma'i bde drod cher 'bar
NK067(ju)001:1064: bas rags rlung gi rgyu ba bcom /
NK067(ju)001:1065: thig le 'gro 'ong med par snying ga'i gnas las
NK067(ju)001:1066: mi g.yo bar gnas pas mtshan 'dzin thams cad mi
NK067(ju)001:1067: rtog pa'i klong du thim pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1069: snying po'i thig le sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:1070: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab gi dbus na mkha' 'gro ma
NK067(ju)001:1071: rngam ma zhes bya ba yi ge am gi rnam
NK067(ju)001:1073: snying ga'i 'od kyis mgrin pa'i thig le zhu ba'i dwangs ma snying gar mched /
NK067(ju)001:1074: dbugs thig ler thim pas rlung dang rtog pa 'gag /
NK067(ju)001:1075: 'khor lo gnyis zhal sbyor ba las drod rlung rtsa
NK067(ju)001:1076: gsum cig tu 'dres pa'i bde gsal rnam par mi
NK067(ju)001:1077: rtog pa'i ye shes skyes pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1079: zag pa med pa'i sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK067(ju)001:1080: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo'i dbus su kun
NK067(ju)001:1081: tu bzang po zla ba'i thig le ham gi rnam
NK067(ju)001:1082: par gnas te / sgom tshul mgrin pa'i thig le'i drod yar song /
NK067(ju)001:1083: spyi bo'i thig le la phog pas 'od du zhu
NK067(ju)001:1084: nas spyi blugs su gyur pas bde ba chen po'i
NK067(ju)001:1085: rang bzhin du gyur te bde gsal rnam par mi
NK067(ju)001:1086: rtog pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs su skyes nas
NK067(ju)001:1087: kun gyi dngos por bdag gyur ba zhes bya ba
NK067(ju)001:1090: 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas dbab bzung
NK067(ju)001:1091: ldog khyab kyi sbyor bas skad cig la bde stong
NK067(ju)001:1092: gnyis med kyi ye shes bskyed pa thabs lam gcig
NK067(ju)001:1093: car ba ste / zhes pas phyag rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa brtag pa /
NK067(ju)001:1096: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa rnams ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK067(ju)001:1097: yab yum lhar bskyed pa lha'i 'du shes /
NK067(ju)001:1098: mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara byin gyis brlab pa sngags kyi 'du shes /
NK067(ju)001:1099: thabs 'di la brten nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK067(ju)001:1100: mngon du bya'o snyam pa chos kyi 'du shes te
NK067(ju)001:1102: brda' bzhis bsnol mar bskul ba sogs ni nye bsnyen /
NK067(ju)001:1103: phyag rgya bzhis gnyis med du rol ba na /
NK067(ju)001:1104: rjes chags kyi rlung bskyod pas dmar cha 'bar ba
NK067(ju)001:1105: des dkar cha zhu ba yas babs kyi 'gros kyis
NK067(ju)001:1106: phyin pa las 'khor lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i rim pas
NK067(ju)001:1107: rdo rje nor bu'i rtser 'dzag med du bzung bas
NK067(ju)001:1108: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK067(ju)001:1110: de lhar dbab bzung gi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)001:1111: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blangs te bzlog pa'i sbyor
NK067(ju)001:1112: bas gyen du drangs te 'khor lo'i gnas so sor
NK067(ju)001:1113: mas brtan gyi dga' ba nyams su myong mthar byang
NK067(ju)001:1114: sems rtsa gnas thams cad du khyab par dgram pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1115: sbyor bas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)001:1116: nyams su myong ba ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK067(ju)001:1117: de ltar yang rtsa rgyud du /
NK067(ju)001:1118: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK067(ju)001:1119: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK067(ju)001:1122: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK067(ju)001:1123: gsang dbang mchog gis sbyin par byed ces so //
NK067(ju)001:1125: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK067(ju)001:1126: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK067(ju)001:1127: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK067(ju)001:1128: ces pas gtso bor thos bsam sgom pas bsdus pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1129: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis rang rgyud la sgrib
NK067(ju)001:1130: par byed pa'i 'ching ba chos nyid du grol bar
NK067(ju)001:1131: byed pa ste / dpe gang gis mtshon na /
NK067(ju)001:1132: rin po che koostu b+ha dang lhan cig bzhag pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1133: rdo'i khams rim gyis gser du 'gyur ba bzhin no
NK067(ju)001:1136: ring ba'am rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:1137: zhes pas thabs lam la ltos na grol lam ring lam du 'gyur bas ring ba zhes smos la /
NK067(ju)001:1138: de la rim gcig car gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:1139: thog mar 'chad bde ba'i phyir gcig car bshad na /
NK067(ju)001:1140: skal ldan dbang po yang rab kha cig lta ba
NK067(ju)001:1141: gtan la 'bebs pa'i skabs su dbyer med chig chod
NK067(ju)001:1142: du rtogs / bar du bsgom pa goms pa'i dus su dbyer med chig chod du goms /
NK067(ju)001:1143: mthar 'bras bu'i dus su'ang dbyer med chig chod du mthar phyin par byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1145: rgyu ni bden gnyis gcig car du //
NK067(ju)001:1146: gcig pas gcig pa'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK067(ju)001:1147: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK067(ju)001:1148: chos kun rang bzhin rtogs pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:1149: skye med dbyings kyi byin brlabsa las //
NK067(ju)001:1150: chos kun snang bar shes pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:1151: de lta bu yi rang bzhin du //
NK067(ju)001:1152: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK067(ju)001:1153: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK067(ju)001:1154: rnal 'byor sa la sleb pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:1157: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK067(ju)001:1158: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK067(ju)001:1160: gnyis pa rim gyis pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:1161: yang rim gyis rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa ni rim gyis pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1166: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK067(ju)001:1167: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK067(ju)001:1168: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK067(ju)001:1169: zhes pas mtshan nyid gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:1170: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK067(ju)001:1171: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK067(ju)001:1175: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK067(ju)001:1177: gzhal bya zhen snang nyid 'jal byed gtan tshig rnams kyis gtan la 'bebs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1180: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig /
NK067(ju)001:1184: tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:1186: sngon byung du ston pa sku lngas /
NK067(ju)001:1187: ston pa chos skus 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho la skye med don gyi gsung gis /
NK067(ju)001:1188: longs skus smin pa brgya mtshor dgongs brdas /
NK067(ju)001:1189: sprul skus mos pa rgya mtshor brjod tshig gis /
NK067(ju)001:1190: rdo rje'i skus dbyer med rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung gis /
NK067(ju)001:1191: mngon byang gis rgyal ba rgya mtsho la rigs pa byin rlabs kyis brda' sprod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1192: rang rang gi 'khor lnga la gsung lnga'i sgo nas
NK067(ju)001:1193: chos nyid kyi don dngos su gtan la 'bebs par
NK067(ju)001:1194: byed pa ste / de nyid las /
NK067(ju)001:1195: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK067(ju)001:1197: gsung lnga bstan pa de kho na //
NK067(ju)001:1201: dbang rnon mchog rnams la snang grags kyi chos 'di dag gis mtshon nas /
NK067(ju)001:1202: dngos lngas gtan la phab pa'i sku lnga'i gsung gi tshul du rtogs par byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1204: rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK067(ju)001:1205: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK067(ju)001:1206: nges lung yin phyir chos tshul ston //
NK067(ju)001:1207: brjod dang 'dra bar brda' sprod pas //
NK067(ju)001:1208: ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)001:1209: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK067(ju)001:1212: sngar gyi tshul lnga nyid tshig tu dngos su brjod pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1214: ngo bo snang tshig rang snang tshig /
NK067(ju)001:1215: ldem dgongs tshig dang bkri drang tshig /
NK067(ju)001:1216: 'dod rkyen tshig dang rdo rje'i tshig /
NK067(ju)001:1217: rang rig mngon gsal tshig gis mtshon //
NK067(ju)001:1220: dpyad du med pas go ba sku bzhi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK067(ju)001:1221: dpyad du yod pas go ba sprul sku'i gtan tshigs gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:1223: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK067(ju)001:1224: mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK067(ju)001:1232: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:1234: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK067(ju)001:1235: byin gyis brlabsa dang mngon sum pa //
NK067(ju)001:1237: rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)001:1239: rang byung gi ye shes su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1240: rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1242: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1243: rol pa 'gag med lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1244: mtshon du med pa'i ye ge a nyid mtshon byed
NK067(ju)001:1245: yi ge du mar ma 'gag par mtshon nas rtogs
NK067(ju)001:1246: pa'i phyir / byin gyis rlabs ni /
NK067(ju)001:1247: rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gag med gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1248: ldog pa so sor snang yang ngo bo dbyer med kyi byin rlabs shugs la 'byung ba yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1249: lhag pa don dam gyi snang ldog kun rdzob sku
NK067(ju)001:1250: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i
NK067(ju)001:1252: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1253: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1254: rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1256: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK067(ju)001:1258: snod bcud rgyud gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1259: ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1260: dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1262: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK067(ju)001:1265: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)001:1266: mnyam pa bzhis 'khor 'das gnyis med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1268: theg chen thun mong pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK067(ju)001:1269: myu gu bdag las skye ba med pa lta bu rnam grangs pa'i don dam dang /
NK067(ju)001:1270: mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang bral ba rnam grangs min pa'i don dam gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1272: spros pa bkag pa'i stong nyid tsam du mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1273: chu zla lta bu log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK067(ju)001:1274: mkha' zla lta bu yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1276: bden pas stong pa tsam du mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1277: thun mong min pa lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK067(ju)001:1278: rnam grangs pa med dgag dang /
NK067(ju)001:1279: rnam pa min pa min dgag gi stong nyid gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1281: lhag pa don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1282: ma dag pa las snang log pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)001:1283: dag pa lhar snang yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1285: lhag pa kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1288: snang lugs du mar snang yang yin lugs nas gzhal na de ltar min te /
NK067(ju)001:1289: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK067(ju)001:1290: po gcig gi bdag nyid du ye nas gnas pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1291: phyir / gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags ni /
NK067(ju)001:1292: tshig mdo sngags thun mong du grags shing don sngags
NK067(ju)001:1293: rang gzhung du gtan la 'bebs pas khyad par du
NK067(ju)001:1299: gnyis pa tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs ni bsgrub bya sgrub5 dug lnga chos can1 /
NK067(ju)001:1301: rang rang gi ngo bo stong pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1302: dper na thag khra sbrul du snang yang gshis la sbrul ma grub pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:1303: 2snang ba phyi nang gi chos thams cad chos can /
NK067(ju)001:1304: spros pa'i mtha' dang de la ltos pa'i dbus sogs cir yang ma dmigs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1305: yang dag par gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1307: rang bzhin du nges pa min te /
NK067(ju)001:1308: dbyibs dang kha dog chos du ma dang ldan pas
NK067(ju)001:1309: phyi yul gyi rnam pa gcig tu sgrub pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)001:1315: yang dag par cir yang ma sgrub pas ci yang min te /
NK067(ju)001:1316: snang tshod du ma 'gags par rang snang bas ci yang yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1317: byed gnyis tha snyad pa'i ngor go bzlog pa'i tshul gyis ston pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1319: des mtshon ci yang yin pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)001:1320: sems chos ci yang ma yin no //
NK067(ju)001:1321: de phyir ma yin kun yin pas //
NK067(ju)001:1322: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK067(ju)001:1324: de ltar gtan la phab pas rtogs bya'i lta ba
NK067(ju)001:1325: rang bzhin rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don de bzhin
NK067(ju)001:1326: nyid de rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang
NK067(ju)001:1327: gsal du rjen par rtogs pa ni grub mtha' ste
NK067(ju)001:1329: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK067(ju)001:1330: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK067(ju)001:1331: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK067(ju)001:1332: rang gsal gsum bral mi 'gul bar //
NK067(ju)001:1333: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK067(ju)001:1334: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK067(ju)001:1338: lta ba khyad par 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)001:1339: rdzogs pa chen po mchog go lo //
NK067(ju)001:1340: sngags kyi khyad chos lta ba min //
NK067(ju)001:1341: dbu ma las lhag ga la yod //
NK067(ju)001:1343: gang dag sngags kyi grub mtha' ni lta ba dbu
NK067(ju)001:1344: ma la thabs khyad par du 'phags pas phye ba
NK067(ju)001:1345: tsam du bzhed pa ni mi rigs te /
NK067(ju)001:1346: dbu ma dang sngags gnyis don dam spros bral dang
NK067(ju)001:1347: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du mnyam par lta bar
NK067(ju)001:1348: mthun na yang de tsam gyis sngags kyi lta ba
NK067(ju)001:1349: gtan la mi phebs pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1351: sngags kyi thun mong min pa'i lta ba ni bden
NK067(ju)001:1352: pa dbyer med snod bcud dag mnyam chen por gtan
NK067(ju)001:1353: la 'bebs dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis so //
NK067(ju)001:1355: khyed cag gis rgyu rgyud de rig pa 'gyur med la de bzhin nyid du byed par 'dug pas /
NK067(ju)001:1356: de 'dra de 'khor lo tha ma'i nges don gyi mdo sde zab mo rnams dang /
NK067(ju)001:1357: de'i dgongs 'grel rgyud bla ma sogs las kyang 'byung
NK067(ju)001:1358: bas rtogs bya'i yul la khyad par med do zhe
NK067(ju)001:1359: na / rig pa 'gyur med la rgyu rgyud du
NK067(ju)001:1360: byed pa 'khor lo tha ma las gsungs pa dang
NK067(ju)001:1362: da dung des sngags kyis thun mong min pa'i lta ba gtan la 'bebs bar mi 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)001:1363: de bzhin nyid de bla na med pa'i rgyud 'dir
NK067(ju)001:1364: rgyu rgyud du 'jog pa'i tshe na lhan cig skyes
NK067(ju)001:1365: pa mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)001:1366: du byas pa ni sngags kyi khyad chos su de
NK067(ju)001:1367: bzhin gshegs pa sras bcas bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)001:1369: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK067(ju)001:1370: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK067(ju)001:1371: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK067(ju)001:1372: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK067(ju)001:1373: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK067(ju)001:1376: srid gsum phra rags gzugs min 'dir ni rnam par shes pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid med de //
NK067(ju)001:1377: sangs rgyas shes rab gang du'ang gnas min zhes pa'i tshig ni sangs rgyas pa rnams ston par 'gyur //
NK067(ju)001:1378: gang gi 'gyur med dang bral mi rnams kyis ni
NK067(ju)001:1379: stong pa nyid do bzung nas stong par lta byed
NK067(ju)001:1380: pa // des na gtso bos gang zhig 'pho med
NK067(ju)001:1381: lhan skyes lus kyi bde ba dag ni sngags kyi
NK067(ju)001:1382: pa // theg par bstan // zhes dang /
NK067(ju)001:1384: dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gro las //
NK067(ju)001:1385: lha dang lha min mi rnams dang //
NK067(ju)001:1386: bshang ba'i srin bu sogs kyis kyang //
NK067(ju)001:1387: bde ba gang phyir mi shes pa //
NK067(ju)001:1388: rtag tu rang bzhin bde ba can //
NK067(ju)001:1389: 'jig rten khams ni gang du yang //
NK067(ju)001:1390: sangs rgyas gzhan du rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK067(ju)001:1391: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK067(ju)001:1392: sangs rgyas gzhan du bstan pa med //
NK067(ju)001:1394: gzhan yang 'phros don gnyis snang 'khor ba'i chos 'di
NK067(ju)001:1395: rnams thag khra'i sbrul ltar med snang glo bur ba
NK067(ju)001:1396: dang / de dag gi snang gzhi gnas lugs de bzhin nyid yin pa'i gnad kyis /
NK067(ju)001:1397: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag par gsungs pa yang /
NK067(ju)001:1398: phung sogs kyi snang gzhi de bzhin nyid kyi rtsal gnyug ma ste /
NK067(ju)001:1399: shin tu phra ba'i ye shes kyi rtsa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1401: ye shes kyi khams zhes sam /
NK067(ju)001:1405: mkha' sems gnyis gnyis zung du 'jug pa rnams rim
NK067(ju)001:1406: par ye nas sku gsum rdo rje gsum gyi ngo
NK067(ju)001:1407: bor gzhan gyis ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa
NK067(ju)001:1408: dang / khams lnga'i dwangs ma ye ji bzhin pa'i rigs lnga dang /
NK067(ju)001:1409: sogs khong nas ye shes kyi khams rigs drug pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1410: bdag nyid du dag pas lha'i bdag nyid du bzhugs
NK067(ju)001:1412: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas lam rim du /
NK067(ju)001:1413: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK067(ju)001:1414: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres gsal //
NK067(ju)001:1417: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la /
NK067(ju)001:1421: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang /
NK067(ju)001:1422: spyi'i rnam pa tsam sgom pa mos sgom dang /
NK067(ju)001:1424: lam so so nas g.yo thob goms brtan gyi nyams mthar phyin par bslab ma nus na yang /
NK067(ju)001:1425: don spyi'i tshul tsam du bsgom pa ni mos sgom ste /
NK067(ju)001:1427: thun gcig la srung 'khor nas bzung cho ga'i bya ba tshar gcig rdzogs par bsgrub pa lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)001:1428: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK067(ju)001:1429: lam kun skad cig chas bsgom na //
NK067(ju)001:1430: spros pa'i 'khor lo mos sgom zhing //
NK067(ju)001:1433: lam so so'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin par bslab pa ni nges rdzogs te /
NK067(ju)001:1435: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK067(ju)001:1436: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK067(ju)001:1437: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK067(ju)001:1438: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK067(ju)001:1439: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK067(ju)001:1440: skyes pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK067(ju)001:1442: gtso bor rdzogs rim gyi sbyang bya bstan kyang /
NK067(ju)001:1443: 'chi bar skye gsum gyi bag chags la phra rags gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:1444: rags pa sbyong byed bskyed rim gyi dbang du byas na /
NK067(ju)001:1445: mar 'chi bar skye gsum dang skye ba la'ang dri
NK067(ju)001:1446: za'i sems mngal du zhugs nas lus rim gyis grub
NK067(ju)001:1448: skyes nas bu tsha 'khor 'dab rgyas pa'i bar dang /
NK067(ju)001:1449: blo gros nar son nas bcad ris dang khe grags sgrub pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1450: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum gyi bag chags sbyong /
NK067(ju)001:1451: yang sangs rgyas chos longs sprul gsum phrin las dang
NK067(ju)001:1452: bcas pa'i rnam pa lam byed kyis rigs kyi nus
NK067(ju)001:1453: pa gsos btab nas 'bras bur rdzogs par byed /
NK067(ju)001:1454: lam gong ma 'od gsal las snying rje chen po'i
NK067(ju)001:1455: 'phen pas zung 'jug gi lhar ldang ba'i smin byed
NK067(ju)001:1456: du 'gro zhing / ji ltar sgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:1457: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs par
NK067(ju)001:1458: bsgom pa de ting stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)001:1459: / de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK067(ju)001:1460: sems can la dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje bsgom
NK067(ju)001:1461: pa kun ting snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor /
NK067(ju)001:1462: de las rgyu ting rang rig a dkar por bsgoms
NK067(ju)001:1463: nas yi ge'i 'phro 'du la sems sbyang ba phra
NK067(ju)001:1465: de las cho ga gsum lta bus lha yab yum
NK067(ju)001:1466: yan lag gi lha dgu dang bcas bsgom pa rags
NK067(ju)001:1467: pa lha sku la bslab pa ste phyag rgya gcig
NK067(ju)001:1470: rtsa lha gnyis la yan lag gi lha dgu dang
NK067(ju)001:1471: bcas bsgoms pas lha nyi shur 'gyur ba'i phyir phyag
NK067(ju)001:1472: rgya gcig par ci'i phyir 'gyur snyam na /
NK067(ju)001:1474: rtsa ba'i lha zung 'jug gi lha sku gcig las mi 'da' ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1475: dper na shing gi sdong po bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:1476: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor la bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:1482: zhi ba la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa rigs lnga rigs
NK067(ju)001:1483: chung dang bcas pa yab yum ste lnga bcu'i steng
NK067(ju)001:1484: du / sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug /
NK067(ju)001:1487: thub drug ste brgyad cu rtsa gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:1493: bsdus pa rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK067(ju)001:1494: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK067(ju)001:1495: khro bo la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum rigs chung bcas lnga bcu'i steng /
NK067(ju)001:1496: gnas yul sgo ma dbang phyug nyer brgyad khro bcu
NK067(ju)001:1497: yab yum nyi shu bsnan pas brgya dang bco brgyad
NK067(ju)001:1498: / 'bring po khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum steng
NK067(ju)001:1499: gnas yul sogs sngar ltar bgrangs pas don brgyad bsdus
NK067(ju)001:1500: pa de dag las khro bcu yab yum nyi shu
NK067(ju)001:1501: phri bas lnga bcu brgyad do //
NK067(ju)001:1503: zhi ba la tshom bu gcig gsum lnga ba gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:1504: mi bskyod pa yab yum la rdo rje rigs kyi rigs chung zung bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)001:1505: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad kyi bdag nyid can ni tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1506: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum yum dang bcas pa rang rang gi rigs chung gi bskor ba la /
NK067(ju)001:1507: khro bo bcu las steng 'og gi khro bo spangs
NK067(ju)001:1508: pa'i yab yum zung brgyad bsnan pa'i zhe drug ni
NK067(ju)001:1510: rigs lnga yab yum rigs chung dang bcas pa la
NK067(ju)001:1511: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste bdun cu ni
NK067(ju)001:1513: khro bo la rtsa rgyud du tshogs sgrub tsam las gsal bar ma gsungs na'ang /
NK067(ju)001:1516: gsum dang lnga ru bsgom par bya //
NK067(ju)001:1517: zhes pas zhi ba dang mtshungs par tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:1518: gsum ka la mtshungs par gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo dang bcas yod pa gzhir bzhag nas /
NK067(ju)001:1519: tshom bu gcig pa'i skabs dbus su rdo rje khrag
NK067(ju)001:1520: 'thung yab yum la rdo rje rigs kyi rigs chung
NK067(ju)001:1521: gi khro bo yab yum bzhis bskor ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:1522: mtha' bskor du khro bcu yab yum nyi shu ste don brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:1523: tshom bu gsum pa'i skabs su de rnams kyi steng
NK067(ju)001:1524: du shar nub tu bud+d+ha pad+ma khrag 'thung yab yum
NK067(ju)001:1525: rigs chung bcas bsnan pa'i go brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:1526: tshom bu lnga pa'i skabs su de'i steng rat+na dang
NK067(ju)001:1527: karma khrag 'thung te rigs chung bcas bsnan pa'i brgya
NK067(ju)001:1528: bco brgyad do // gsum pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:1529: snang ba rnam 'byed la bslabs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1530: de la'ang zhi khro gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:1534: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1536: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1537: de yang mi bskyod pa la mtshon na /
NK067(ju)001:1538: bdag nyid mi bskyod pa yab yum du gsal ba'i
NK067(ju)001:1539: yab kyi yan lag lnga la byed po dang rgyal
NK067(ju)001:1540: ba rigs bzhi / mig rna ba sna lce bzhii'i g.yas kyi cha la nang sems dang /
NK067(ju)001:1541: g.yon gyi cha la phyi sems bzhi /
NK067(ju)001:1542: rkang lag gi mthil bzhir sgo ba bzhi rnams dang /
NK067(ju)001:1543: yum gyi gnas de rnams su sngar gyi yum rnams bsgom /
NK067(ju)001:1545: mtshog ma la sogs pa'i gnas drug tu thub pa drug ste /
NK067(ju)001:1546: de ltar yab yum bsdoms pas yan lag gi lha
NK067(ju)001:1547: bzhi bcu ni rags pa dang phyir gnas pa'i cha
NK067(ju)001:1549: de rnams la shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu /
NK067(ju)001:1550: de dag las thabs lha bzhi bcu po re re
NK067(ju)001:1551: la sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum ste brgya
NK067(ju)001:1552: nyi shu / thabs lha dang byin rlabs kyi lha
NK067(ju)001:1553: ba sdoms pa brgya drug cu po re re la
NK067(ju)001:1554: dbang lha lnga lnga ste brgyad brgya /
NK067(ju)001:1555: kun dril bas chig stong ngo //
NK067(ju)001:1556: gnyis pa ni mi bskyod pa la ji ltar sgom pa bzhin du /
NK067(ju)001:1560: sgo ba bzhi ste yab yum zung bcu bdun dang /
NK067(ju)001:1561: thub pa drug re re la yang bsgoms pas nyi khri bzhi stong ste /
NK067(ju)001:1562: rtsa lha gang yin gyi rtog pa'i gnas su byed po spo ba khyad par ro //
NK067(ju)001:1564: mi bskyod pas gtso bo byas pa'i dkyil 'khor la
NK067(ju)001:1565: yan lag gi lha ji ltar bsgom pa bzhin du
NK067(ju)001:1566: shar gyi glo 'bur la rnam snang gis gtso byas
NK067(ju)001:1567: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa sogs rigs
NK067(ju)001:1568: 'gre bas bsam gyi mi khyab par spro ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:1571: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu /
NK067(ju)001:1572: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:1575: yan lag bkod pa lnga bcu brgyad //
NK067(ju)001:1576: cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang //
NK067(ju)001:1577: dgu bcu'i lha rnams yan lag ldan //
NK067(ju)001:1578: zhes pas gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka'i yan lag lnga khrag 'thung yab lnga dang /
NK067(ju)001:1580: yab kyi dbang rten gyi nang rtsar goo r+ai ma brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:1583: mjing 'jug gi tshigs bsnan pa'i rgal tshigs nyer brgyad
NK067(ju)001:1584: la dbang mo nyer brgyad de thabs lha nga brgyad
NK067(ju)001:1585: / de rnams la ye shes sems dpa' dang sku
NK067(ju)001:1586: gsung thugs kyi lha rnams re re bsgoms pas nga
NK067(ju)001:1587: brgyad pa cha lnga la nyis brgyad dang dgu bcu
NK067(ju)001:1588: / / de las shes rab kyi lha nga brgyad
NK067(ju)001:1589: phri ba'i lhag nyis brgya so gnyis po re re
NK067(ju)001:1590: la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste chig brgya
NK067(ju)001:1591: drug cu byung ba nyis brgya dgu bcu la bsnan
NK067(ju)001:1592: pa'i stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu'o //
NK067(ju)001:1594: khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum zung lnga la sngar ltar dang /
NK067(ju)001:1595: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo rnams la mgo'i g.yas dang /
NK067(ju)001:1596: rkang lag g.yas kyi mdun rgyab la yab lnga dang /
NK067(ju)001:1598: rkang lag g.yon gyi mdun rgyab la yum lnga bkod
