NK067(ju)001:1599: de lha re re la stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu
NK067(ju)001:1600: bsgom pa'i nges pas bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya
NK067(ju)001:1602: sngar zhi ba'i skabs su bshad pas mtshon no //
NK067(ju)001:1604: zhi khro gnyis ka la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:1605: zhi ba la rgyas pa bshad rgyud rdo rje nas
NK067(ju)001:1606: thub drug dang yum rnams ma gtogs thams cad zhal
NK067(ju)001:1608: 'bring po rigs lnga'am gtso bo tsam zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK067(ju)001:1609: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1610: khro bo la gtso bo dbu phyag grangs med pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1611: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa /
NK067(ju)001:1612: cha mthun gyi rgyud lha mo sgyu d+r+wa nas gnas
NK067(ju)001:1613: yul gyi ma mo sogs kyang zhal gsum phyag drug
NK067(ju)001:1615: da lta phyag bzhes su rgyas pa la rigs lnga zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK067(ju)001:1617: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1618: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor la /
NK067(ju)001:1619: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK067(ju)001:1620: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba /
NK067(ju)001:1621: 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa dang gsum /
NK067(ju)001:1623: dang po gang du sgrub pa'i gnas ni /
NK067(ju)001:1624: bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas su tshogs kyi
NK067(ju)001:1625: khang pa steng 'og dang 'khor rim pa sum ldan
NK067(ju)001:1626: rtsig pa la chu tshon gyi tshom bu gang sgom
NK067(ju)001:1628: gnyis pa gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus ni /
NK067(ju)001:1629: yar gyi tshes brgyad rgyu skar rgyal dang ldan pa
NK067(ju)001:1630: la sogs pa gza' skar shis pa'i dus nas sgrub
NK067(ju)001:1632: 'bras bu 'grub pa'i dus ni 'og tu 'chad do //
NK067(ju)001:1633: gsum pa gang la brten nas sgrub pa'i yo byad ni /
NK067(ju)001:1637: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad rnams spogs chog ldang tshod du bsag pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1638: bzhi pa sgrub pa po la gang gis sgrub pa'i ston pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1639: gang dang lhan cig sgrub pa'i 'khor gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:1641: tshogs kyi rdo rje slob dpon yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1643: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK067(ju)001:1644: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK067(ju)001:1646: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu bsten //
NK067(ju)001:1649: slob dpon dang dgongs pa mnyam pa'i rdo rje rgyal tshab /
NK067(ju)001:1650: skad gdangs che zhing las khrigs mkhas pa'i rdo rje las mkhan /
NK067(ju)001:1651: sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa'i las bzhi'i gzungs ma /
NK067(ju)001:1652: mi ma yin mthong ba'i mig rnon gyis nyul le
NK067(ju)001:1653: shes shing ting 'dzin las rung gis bzlog nus pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1655: drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog /
NK067(ju)001:1656: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i rdo rje ging /
NK067(ju)001:1657: kha bskang zhing g.yos la mkhas pa'i rdo rje byan po /
NK067(ju)001:1658: phyi nang gi brda' sbyor mkhas pa'i rdo rje rdul
NK067(ju)001:1659: chags skyes bu sogs tshom bur 'brel ba'i 'khor lo
NK067(ju)001:1660: / lnga pa sgrub chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:1661: spros bcas man chad la brtan pa thob pa zhig
NK067(ju)001:1662: gis 'og nas 'byung ba'i bsnyen sgrub kyi sgo nas
NK067(ju)001:1663: sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1665: sngar bshad pa'i gnas su dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas
NK067(ju)001:1666: so sor rnal 'byor pa pho mo dang lha yab
NK067(ju)001:1667: yum brang sprad de so sor 'dug nas rim pa
NK067(ju)001:1668: gshoms dang 'brel bar nub dang po 'go 'dzin gyi
NK067(ju)001:1669: bsnyen pa nas bzung bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i rim
NK067(ju)001:1672: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK067(ju)001:1673: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK067(ju)001:1675: skabs 'dir bskyed rim gyi dbang du byas te /
NK067(ju)001:1676: gtso 'khor gang yin de'i lha so so'i nga rgyal
NK067(ju)001:1677: brtan po la sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa sor
NK067(ju)001:1678: bzhag nas / nub dang po 'go 'dzin gyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1679: ji tsam sgrub pa'i zhag grangs phyed tshun chad nye
NK067(ju)001:1680: bsnyen te de gnyis la 'od zer dkar po'i 'phro
NK067(ju)001:1681: 'du bsnol mas rgyud dag par byed pa nye bsnyen
NK067(ju)001:1682: dang / nub tha ma ma gtogs pa'i phyed phan
NK067(ju)001:1683: chad 'od zer dmar po'i 'phro 'dus dngos grub bskul
NK067(ju)001:1684: zhing bsdu bas bcud dag par byed pa sgrub pa
NK067(ju)001:1685: dang / dang / nub tha mar 'od zer mthing
NK067(ju)001:1686: ga tshur bsdu bas rgyud dag par byed pa'i sgo
NK067(ju)001:1687: nas srod kyi cha las lha la dngos grub blang
NK067(ju)001:1688: dang / dang / / nas gung gi tshe ta
NK067(ju)001:1689: na sgrol ba'i mdzad spyod kyis dgra las dngos grub
NK067(ju)001:1690: dang / dang / / blang / tho rengs yum
NK067(ju)001:1691: dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i sgo nas a
NK067(ju)001:1692: li'i mdzad spyod kyis yum gyi mkha' las dngos grub
NK067(ju)001:1693: len pa sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK067(ju)001:1694: zla gcig la dper mtshon na /
NK067(ju)001:1696: zla phyed phyed zhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK067(ju)001:1698: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK067(ju)001:1700: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK067(ju)001:1701: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK067(ju)001:1704: de ltar zla ba drug spogs chog dang bcas pas rig 'dzin gyi 'bras bu 'grub pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1705: 'di bskyed rim yin pas rig 'dzin kyang thun mong
NK067(ju)001:1706: gi dngos grub las rgya dang ye rgya'i khyad par
NK067(ju)001:1707: gyis 'dod pa dang gzugs kyi lha dang skal pa
NK067(ju)001:1708: mnyam pa'i rigs 'dzin la sbyor ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:1709: da ni lam gyi gzhung shing rdzogs rim ltar bshad na /
NK067(ju)001:1710: 'chi ba 'od gsal dang rjes mthun stong pa chen po /
NK067(ju)001:1711: bar do dang snying rje sgyu ma /
NK067(ju)001:1712: skyes pa'i rim pa dang po dang phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK067(ju)001:1714: gsum pa dang tshogs sgrub ste lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:1716: lus can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe 'byung ba lnga dang
NK067(ju)001:1717: dkar dmar nag po'i lam gsum rim par thim pas
NK067(ju)001:1718: rnam par mi rtog pa'i 'od gsal 'char te /
NK067(ju)001:1720: 'gro ba ma lus thams cad dag /
NK067(ju)001:1721: gnas pa'i stobs ni zad pa na //
NK067(ju)001:1722: 'dus pa lnga yi rim pa yis //
NK067(ju)001:1723: bag chags snyigs ma rang zad nas //
NK067(ju)001:1724: 'od gsal stong par snang ba na //
NK067(ju)001:1725: re dogs med pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK067(ju)001:1727: de'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir de dang rnam pa mthun pa'i lam sgom tshul yang /
NK067(ju)001:1728: lta ba gtan la 'beb pa gzhir bzhag ste /
NK067(ju)001:1729: bsam gtan la tsher ma mi 'byung ba'i gnas su
NK067(ju)001:1730: lus gnad rnam par snang mdzad kyi chos bdun dang
NK067(ju)001:1731: ldan pas / rig pa ma bcos pa'i ngang du so mar 'jog pa rig pa spyi blugs dang /
NK067(ju)001:1732: sngar thos bsam gyi lta ba dran par byas nas
NK067(ju)001:1733: de'i ngang du 'jog pa mthong ba'i rjes la 'jog
NK067(ju)001:1734: pa ste / 'jog thabs gnyis gang rung gis don
NK067(ju)001:1735: dam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting 'dzin la mnyam
NK067(ju)001:1736: par 'jog pa nyin mo'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK067(ju)001:1737: mtshan mo gnyid 'thug gi 'od gsal 'dzin pa'i man
NK067(ju)001:1738: ngag nyid sbrel te nyin mtshan kha sbyor du nyams
NK067(ju)001:1739: su len pa'i sgo nas nyams lnga mthar phyin par
NK067(ju)001:1740: bslab pa'o // gnyis pa snying rje sgyu ma ni /
NK067(ju)001:1741: sngar gyi 'chi kha'i 'od gsal ngos ma zin pa
NK067(ju)001:1742: las snang gsum dang 'byung ba'i bgrod pa go bzlog
NK067(ju)001:1743: gi tshul du langs te bar do'i yid lus sgyu
NK067(ju)001:1746: bar ma sgyu ma'i lus thob pas //
NK067(ju)001:1747: ma spangs longs spyod rdzogs par bshad //
NK067(ju)001:1749: de'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir rjes mthun gyi lam sgom tshul yang /
NK067(ju)001:1750: sngar gyi stong chen 'od gsal gyi ngang du sems 'gags pas /
NK067(ju)001:1755: dkar dmar nag po'i lam gsum la sogs pa'i stong
NK067(ju)001:1756: gzugs kyi snang ba shar ba nyid gyi rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)001:1757: sad pa'i snang ba de dag dang /
NK067(ju)001:1758: mtshan mo rmii lam gyi snang ba thams cad sgyu
NK067(ju)001:1759: ma chu zla ltar mthong ba las dmigs med bde
NK067(ju)001:1760: chen gyi snying rje ma 'gags par shar ba la
NK067(ju)001:1762: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:1763: skyes pa'i rim pa dang po'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK067(ju)001:1764: snang ba ris med las snying rje chen po'i 'phen pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:1765: ting nge 'dzin gyi rkyen gyi chu dwangs pa la
NK067(ju)001:1766: gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan
NK067(ju)001:1767: du byung ba'i lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa rang
NK067(ju)001:1768: shar gyis snang ba thams cad la rgyas thebs pa'o
NK067(ju)001:1769: // bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas ni /
NK067(ju)001:1770: skyes pa'i rim pa bar ma'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1771: de dang rjes mthun gyi lam ste /
NK067(ju)001:1772: sngar gyi lha snang de las ches cher 'phel bas
NK067(ju)001:1773: snang ba thams cad zung 'jug gi lha gtso 'khor
NK067(ju)001:1774: dang tshom bu'i rnam par mngon sum du spros te
NK067(ju)001:1775: ma 'dres yongs su 'char ba la goms par byed
NK067(ju)001:1776: pa'o // lnga pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub ni /
NK067(ju)001:1777: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum pa'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1778: de dang rjes mthun gyi lam ste /
NK067(ju)001:1779: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gi sgo
NK067(ju)001:1780: nas spros bcas bskyed rim dang phyogs mthun du sgrub
NK067(ju)001:1781: pa'am / spros med rnal 'byor pho mo gtso bo yab yum tsam tshogs pa la brten pa'am /
NK067(ju)001:1782: shin tu spros med ni yab mi 'gyur ba'i bde
NK067(ju)001:1783: chen nyid yum rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa
NK067(ju)001:1784: nyid kha sbyor gyis sgrub pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1786: dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi dbye bas zla ba drug gam lo gcig /
NK067(ju)001:1787: lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:1788: lo gcig zla ba bzhi rnams kyis nang gi mngon
NK067(ju)001:1789: byang lnga la brten nas zag med mthong lam rnam
NK067(ju)001:1790: gnyis gang rung la sbyor bar byed de /
NK067(ju)001:1792: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK067(ju)001:1793: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK067(ju)001:1794: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK067(ju)001:1796: da ni zag ldog yod med kyi mu bzhi brtsi bar bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:1797: de la zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i mu /
NK067(ju)001:1798: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i mu /
NK067(ju)001:1799: zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i mu /
NK067(ju)001:1800: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i mu'o //
NK067(ju)001:1805: phyag rgya gcig spros te tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:1807: de phyir lam bzhir zag ldog yod //
NK067(ju)001:1810: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste /
NK067(ju)001:1811: spyod pa'i dus grangs nges pas zag med la dngos
NK067(ju)001:1812: su sbyor ba'i bar chad med pa ma yin pa'i
NK067(ju)001:1814: dman lam sngon du song ba'i 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK067(ju)001:1815: pa sngags kyi tshogs lam la gnas pa lta bu
NK067(ju)001:1816: ste / de ni rang don yid byed kyi bsam pas ldog pa srid pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1818: ji srid sa brgyad ma thob bar //
NK067(ju)001:1819: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jig /
NK067(ju)001:1822: slob pa'i zung 'jug rig 'dzin bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:1824: zag kun zad pa'i rigs chen 'di //
NK067(ju)001:1825: ji ltar spyad kyang ldog pa med //
NK067(ju)001:1827: 'o na zag pa zhes bya ba gang la zer na /
NK067(ju)001:1828: spyir mngon pa sogs las zag pa'i sgo drug bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)001:1829: skabs 'dir zag pa'i gtso bo dang /
NK067(ju)001:1832: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i las kyi khams gsum du zag cing 'pho ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:1834: de dag 'jig rten pa la yod pa ni 'dzin pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur la /
NK067(ju)001:1837: lus rang dbang med par 'dor ba lus kyi dang /
NK067(ju)001:1838: bde mi bde rang dbang med par myong ba khams kyi dang /
NK067(ju)001:1839: rang dbang med par lus len pa skye gnas kyi zag pa dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:1840: gsum pa lam 'gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi ni /
NK067(ju)001:1841: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam mthong sgom mthar lam gsum gyis bsdus pa rig 'dzin bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:1842: de yang mthong lam pa la /
NK067(ju)001:1843: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang blo'i nus stobs
NK067(ju)001:1844: che chung gis 'byung ba snyigs ma'i lus ye shes
NK067(ju)001:1845: kyi mes sbyong bar ma nus pa rnam smin rig
NK067(ju)001:1846: 'dzin dang / sbyong bar nus pas skye 'jig med
NK067(ju)001:1847: pa dwangs ma'i lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs
NK067(ju)001:1848: su gyur pa'i tshe dbang gnyis te /
NK067(ju)001:1850: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:1851: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK067(ju)001:1853: de la rnam smin rig 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)001:1854: lus rnam smin sha khrag gi phung po dang ma bral ba /
NK067(ju)001:1855: yid 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin pa /
NK067(ju)001:1856: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin lus rgya dang bral ma
NK067(ju)001:1857: thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor nges
NK067(ju)001:1858: pa ste / chos gsum dang ldan pa yin no //
NK067(ju)001:1859: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK067(ju)001:1860: yid kyis lha yi gzugs bzung zhing //
NK067(ju)001:1861: lus kyi rgya mdun grol gyur na //
NK067(ju)001:1862: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pas //
NK067(ju)001:1863: rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK067(ju)001:1866: bdag don du bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi bya bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed cing /
NK067(ju)001:1867: phrin las bzhi'i sgo nas gzhan don rdzogs par byed /
NK067(ju)001:1868: zag med lha'i spyan rnam par dag pa la sogs pa'i yon tan dang ldan la /
NK067(ju)001:1869: gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten tsam du skus don mdzad cing /
NK067(ju)001:1870: sprul gzugs ston tshul tshe dbang dang cha 'dra bas don mdzad do //
NK067(ju)001:1872: rnam smin gyis lus dwangs ma'i skur bsgyur ma nus pas mthong lam du ci'i phyir 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:1874: byang chub sems dpa' dbang rtul gyi zag bcas kyi
NK067(ju)001:1875: lus sa bdun pa'i bar 'gro bar mdo las bshad
NK067(ju)001:1876: pa bzhin no // tshe dbang rig 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)001:1877: sems 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin cing phra yang
NK067(ju)001:1878: la sogs pa'i 'ja' lus kyi yon tan khyad par
NK067(ju)001:1879: can dang ldan pa'i rdo rje'i lus can te /
NK067(ju)001:1881: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:1882: tshogs spyod sgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK067(ju)001:1883: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK067(ju)001:1884: rdo rje'i lus 'gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK067(ju)001:1887: sman gyi bcud len la brten pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)001:1888: thig le dbab bzung sogs la brten pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)001:1889: sgrol ma rlung la brten pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)001:1890: lam chog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang bzhi las /
NK067(ju)001:1892: zag med mthong lam gyi ye shes ji lta ba bzhin mngon sum du mthong ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1894: bdag don du kun 'gro'i dri ma sbyong zhing /
NK067(ju)001:1895: gzhan don du cho 'phrul bzhi dang phrin las bzhi sogs kyi don mdzad /
NK067(ju)001:1897: mi dang 'dod gzugs kyi lha'i gtso bo'i cha byad du ston pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1899: lha mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin //
NK067(ju)001:1901: de yang lha mi gzhan dang khyad par che ste /
NK067(ju)001:1903: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK067(ju)001:1904: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK067(ju)001:1905: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK067(ju)001:1906: cha byad de nyid kyis chos ston /
NK067(ju)001:1908: mngon shes kyi yul don yang /
NK067(ju)001:1909: dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgyar dus gcig tu don mdzad do //
NK067(ju)001:1911: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku can phyag chen rig 'dzin te /
NK067(ju)001:1913: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK067(ju)001:1914: bsgom pa gang yin mngon 'gyur sku //
NK067(ju)001:1915: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK067(ju)001:1916: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK067(ju)001:1918: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK067(ju)001:1919: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK067(ju)001:1921: de la yang snga ma las /
NK067(ju)001:1922: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK067(ju)001:1926: sngar rang nyid kyis gang bsgoms kyi lhag pa'i lha
NK067(ju)001:1927: rigs lnga gang yin gyi cha lugs 'dzin par 'chad
NK067(ju)001:1928: pa'am yang na bsgom lam sa gnyis pa nas bcu
NK067(ju)001:1929: pa tsam gyi bar sa dgu la rim par sbyar
NK067(ju)001:1930: te / sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i bar bzhi la rdo rje'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:1931: rtogs pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bus rang sa'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:1932: sa drug par sher phyin gtso bor spyod cing chos 'khor bskor ba'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)001:1933: sa bdun pa'ang thabs mkhas pa 'khor lo ltar gyur
NK067(ju)001:1934: pas sa de gnyis 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin zhes bya'o
NK067(ju)001:1935: // brgyad par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la dbang thob bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK067(ju)001:1936: dgu par chags pa med pas zhing sbyong zhing don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK067(ju)001:1937: bcu par phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems can
NK067(ju)001:1938: gyi don byed pa'i phyir ral gri'i rig 'dzin no
NK067(ju)001:1939: // cha byad zung 'jug lha'i sku mtshan dpe rdzogs
NK067(ju)001:1940: pa'i bdag nyid can bdag don du lhan cig gnas
NK067(ju)001:1942: gzhan don du rngon pa dang smad 'tshong ma la
NK067(ju)001:1943: sogs pa gang 'dul gyi sprul gzugs su ston par
NK067(ju)001:1945: mnyam bzhag ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK067(ju)001:1947: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK067(ju)001:1948: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK067(ju)001:1950: mngon shes kyi yul don yang /
NK067(ju)001:1951: dbang shes nyer lnga'i yon tan dang ldan pa tshe dbang dang 'dra na'ang /
NK067(ju)001:1952: 'dir gsal brtan gyi khyad par du byas shing /
NK067(ju)001:1953: longs sku'i zhing dang mnyam par don byed de /
NK067(ju)001:1955: drug dang lnga yi yan lag bcas //
NK067(ju)001:1956: shes pa'ang 'dra mod bzhi sogs kun //
NK067(ju)001:1957: de snyed yul gyi khyad par dang //
NK067(ju)001:1958: don rdzogs mthu dang gdul byas spags //
NK067(ju)001:1960: de ltar sa bcu tsam sgom lam du bsdus nas
NK067(ju)001:1961: rgyun mtha'i ye shes dag las rnam grol lam dang
NK067(ju)001:1962: / khyad par lam ni mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin te /
NK067(ju)001:1963: yan lag bdun dang ldan pa'i ye shes gong ma'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:1965: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang gi cha lugs 'dzin pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:1966: drug pa'i rgyal tshab mdzad pa po gsang ba'i bdag po bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:1967: spyod tshul ni bdag don du rdo rje lta bu'i
NK067(ju)001:1968: ting nge 'dzin bya ba nang gi mngon byang gis
NK067(ju)001:1969: shes sgrib phra ba snang gsum gyi dri ma sbyong
NK067(ju)001:1970: zhing / gzhan don rjes thob la sangs rgyas dang cha 'dra bar 'gro ba'i don mdzad /
NK067(ju)001:1971: sprul gzugs kyang mdzad pa bcu gnyis sogs mchog gi sprul sku dang phyogs mthun du ston /
NK067(ju)001:1972: mngon shes kyi yul don ji snyed mkhyen pa'i yul
NK067(ju)001:1973: rgyal ba nyid dang shas cher 'dra ba'i phyir nam
NK067(ju)001:1974: mkhas khyab tshad kyi don yang ci rigs par mdzad
NK067(ju)001:1976: de ltar dag pa'i shes pa nyid //
NK067(ju)001:1977: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK067(ju)001:1978: lhun mnyam ngang las mi g.yo zhing //
NK067(ju)001:1979: mi rtog nyid du bzhugs pa'ang //
NK067(ju)001:1980: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK067(ju)001:1981: skad cig nyid las rig 'dzin mtha' 'o //
NK067(ju)001:1983: nyid phyir rdo rje 'dzin rdzogs la //
NK067(ju)001:1984: skad cig dus kyis bslab rdzogs nas //
NK067(ju)001:1985: tha ma'i bag la nyal ba dang //
NK067(ju)001:1986: bcom ldan 'das par gyur pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:1987: de tshe de sgrib cha yod kyang //
NK067(ju)001:1988: lhun grub rig 'dzin sar bzhugs nas //
NK067(ju)001:1989: zhing khams thug pa med pa dag /
NK067(ju)001:1990: 'dul phyir sprul sku'i mdzad pa ston //
NK067(ju)001:1992: zhar byung rgyu'i theg pa'i 'phags pa rnams dang dgongs
NK067(ju)001:1993: pa mnyam tshul dang sa'i mo tshod mthun tshul bshad
NK067(ju)001:1995: rgyu'i theg pa'i mthong lam rab dga' la gnas pa'i sems dpa' gnyis dgongs pa mnyam zhing /
NK067(ju)001:1996: de las gzhan pa tshe dbang sogs gsum gyi rgyu'i theg pa'i sa dang po dang /
NK067(ju)001:1998: bcu pa tsam du skal pa mnyam pa ste lam gyi mo tshod mtshungs mod /
NK067(ju)001:1999: 'on kyang dgongs spyod kyis rgyu'i theg pa'i sa de
NK067(ju)001:2000: dag gi byang sems las khyad par du gyur pa
NK067(ju)001:2001: yin te / rgyu'i theg pa'i sgom lam sa brgyad pa dang tshe dbang /
NK067(ju)001:2003: mi slob pa'i kun tu 'od dang lhun grub rig 'dzin rnams mnyam par bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:2004: de ltar yang lam chung las /
NK067(ju)001:2005: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK067(ju)001:2006: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog de //
NK067(ju)001:2007: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK067(ju)001:2008: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK067(ju)001:2009: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK067(ju)001:2011: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi rang 'grel las /
NK067(ju)001:2012: kun tu 'od bsti gnas kyi sa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2013: de ni 'dir lhun gyi sa grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos so //
NK067(ju)001:2015: da ni thod rgal 'byung mi 'byung gi sa mtshams 'chad de /
NK067(ju)001:2016: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi dngos 'bras rgya chen du nges pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:2017: mthong lam gnyis po lam mthar chags kyi skabs su'ang rim par bgrod pa mi srid cing /
NK067(ju)001:2018: rnam smin nas thod rgal du bgrod pa yang mi 'byung ste /
NK067(ju)001:2019: thod rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum ma tshang ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:2022: ngang gis blo chung bas thod rgal mi 'byung ngo zhes bzhed pa yod mod /
NK067(ju)001:2023: de ni skabs 'dir dgongs pa mnyam par ma bzhag par mngon te /
NK067(ju)001:2024: de lta na phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis nas thod rgal 'byung ngam mi 'byung /
NK067(ju)001:2026: rig 'dzin gyi sa la bzhugs pa'i byang sems 'phags
NK067(ju)001:2027: pa las blo che ba'i so skye yod par thal
NK067(ju)001:2028: / phyag rgya gcig spros dang rnam smin gnyis zung 'jug gi lam sgom pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2029: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod par phyogs mtshungs pa gang zhig /
NK067(ju)001:2030: gcig spros la thod rgal 'byung zhing rnam smin la mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)001:2032: zag bcas kyi lam pa thod rgal du bgrod pa mi srid par thal /
NK067(ju)001:2035: 'phags pa ji ltar dbang po rtul kyang so skyes 'gran par nus pa min te /
NK067(ju)001:2037: rang gi dngos 'bras phyag chen nyid du nges pa'i
NK067(ju)001:2038: phyir lam gzhan bar nas bor du med pas thod
NK067(ju)001:2041: gzhan du na cig car ba'i rigs min pa'i lam
NK067(ju)001:2042: pa blo che ba 'ga' zhig phyag rgya gcig spros
NK067(ju)001:2044: tshe dbang nas lhun grub rig 'dzin tshe dbang dang
NK067(ju)001:2045: rgya chen gnyis nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sar
NK067(ju)001:2046: lam gzhan bar nas bor la thod rgal du sbyor
NK067(ju)001:2048: de dag la ngang gis blo che ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2049: zung 'jug gi lam sgom pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2050: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod pa ste thod
NK067(ju)001:2051: rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum po tshang ba'i phyir ro
NK067(ju)001:2052: // de ltar na tshogs sgrub nas kyang thod rgal 'byung ba srid dam snyam na min te /
NK067(ju)001:2054: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK067(ju)001:2055: zhes zag med kyi lam gyi 'du sa dang dbye
NK067(ju)001:2056: sa mthong lam yin par gsungs pas lam gzhan bar
NK067(ju)001:2057: nas bor du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:2058: gsum pa gang du mthar phyin 'bras bu'i rgyud ni /
NK067(ju)001:2059: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK067(ju)001:2061: lhun grub ji bzhin mngon byas pa'ang //
NK067(ju)001:2062: btags pa tsam ste gnyis pa med //
NK067(ju)001:2063: de phyir de la de brjod do //
NK067(ju)001:2064: zhes pas de la sbyang gzhi ni /
NK067(ju)001:2065: rgyu rgyud bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po gdod ma nas rang chas su bzhugs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2066: 'dam gyi dbus na bzhugs pa'i nor bu rin po che bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:2068: med snang glo bur gyi dri ma phra zhing phra ba dang bcas pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2069: nor bu la sgrib par byed pa'i 'dam rdzab bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:2071: rim pa gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i lam rnams te /
NK067(ju)001:2072: bkru byed kyi chu dang 'dag rdzas bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:2074: de ltar lam gyi dri ma sbyangs pa las gzhi
NK067(ju)001:2075: la ji ltar yod pa'i yon tan mngon du gyur
NK067(ju)001:2077: 'dam rdzab las grol ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK067(ju)001:2078: rin po che las 'dod rgu'i char 'bebs pa bzhin
NK067(ju)001:2079: no // nges tshig ni ci'i phyir 'bras bu'i rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)001:2081: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK067(ju)001:2082: ces pas bla na med pa mchog gi 'bras bu
NK067(ju)001:2083: mthar thug pa don du gnyer ba rnams bsam pa
NK067(ju)001:2084: yongs rdzogs pas na 'bras bu dang /
NK067(ju)001:2085: nam yang rgyun mi chad pas na rgyud do //
NK067(ju)001:2088: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK067(ju)001:2089: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NK067(ju)001:2090: de yang skabs kyis lnga lnga ste //
NK067(ju)001:2091: zhes pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga
NK067(ju)001:2092: re re la'ang lnga lngar phye bas 'bras chos nyi
NK067(ju)001:2094: de la sku lnga ni chos sku /
NK067(ju)001:2100: chos sku brjod med don gyi gsung /
NK067(ju)001:2101: longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung /
NK067(ju)001:2102: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung /
NK067(ju)001:2103: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK067(ju)001:2104: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2106: chos kyi sku'i thugs chos dbyings ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:2107: longs sku'i thugs mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:2108: sprul sku'i thugs bya grub ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:2109: mngon byang gi thugs me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK067(ju)001:2110: rdo rje'i thugs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2112: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams /
NK067(ju)001:2113: rgya tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK067(ju)001:2115: khyad par du 'phags pa'i gdan khri /
NK067(ju)001:2116: dgyes rgur spyod pa'i longs spyod dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2122: lhun gyis grub pa ste lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2126: mdzad pa phrin las gsum du 'du ba yin pas /
NK067(ju)001:2129: dbyings rnam dag gi thog tu rig pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)001:2130: sgrib pa las grol bas zung 'jug sku gsum ye
NK067(ju)001:2131: rdzogs mtshan 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad dang bral
NK067(ju)001:2132: ba'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa chos kyi sku dang
NK067(ju)001:2133: / de las ma g.yos bzhin du sa bcu rgyun
NK067(ju)001:2134: mtha' la bzhugs pa'i byang sems rnams la mtshan dpe'i
NK067(ju)001:2135: rnam par snang ba'i gzugs brnyan longs sku dang /
NK067(ju)001:2136: so skye rnams la so so'i mos pa dang mthun par mchog gi sprul sku dang /
NK067(ju)001:2137: bzo dang skye ba sogs gang la gang 'tshams par
NK067(ju)001:2138: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs brnyan ci rigs su snang ba
NK067(ju)001:2139: sprul pa'i sku ste sku gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:2141: sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres par snang ba'i ldog cha nas mngon byang dang /
NK067(ju)001:2142: sku gsum po ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha
NK067(ju)001:2143: nas rdo rje'i sku ste gnyis po bsnan pas sku
NK067(ju)001:2144: lnga'o // skabs 'dir zur pa rnams chos longs sprul gsum sku mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2145: mngon byang dang rdo rje'i sku gnyis te gsum gyi rnam pa'i ldog pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2146: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas bzhag pas sku btags pa ba yin gsung /
NK067(ju)001:2150: rdo rje'i sku gsum po sangs rgyas rang snang gi sku yin pas mtshan nyid pa yin la /
NK067(ju)001:2151: skabs 'di'i longs sku dang sprul sku gnyis gdul bya
NK067(ju)001:2152: gzhan snang yin pas sku btags pa ba'o zhes gsung
NK067(ju)001:2153: ste legs so // gnyis pa brten pa ye shes ni /
NK067(ju)001:2154: de ltar sku lnga mngon du byas pa de'i tshe
NK067(ju)001:2155: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pa
NK067(ju)001:2157: kun gzhi 'byed pa med pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK067(ju)001:2158: gnas su dag pa cir yang mi dmigs pas spros
NK067(ju)001:2159: pa'i mtha' thams cad las 'das pa chos dbyings ye
NK067(ju)001:2160: shes dang / kun gzhi'i rnam shes gsal la rnam
NK067(ju)001:2161: par mi rtog pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su
NK067(ju)001:2162: dag pa me long ngos gnyis pa ltar rang bzhin
NK067(ju)001:2163: gyis chos rnams gsal la spu ris 'byed par mi
NK067(ju)001:2164: mdzad pa me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK067(ju)001:2165: nyon yid kyi phyi nang gi chos rnams la blang
NK067(ju)001:2166: dor byed pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag
NK067(ju)001:2167: pa 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam nyid du
NK067(ju)001:2168: gzigs bas srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa
NK067(ju)001:2170: rnam shes drug 'gags ma thag pa'i yid kyis dpyod
NK067(ju)001:2171: pa med par rtog pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas
NK067(ju)001:2172: su dag pa chos can ma lus pa mngon sum
NK067(ju)001:2173: du ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su sa ler gzigs pa
NK067(ju)001:2174: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK067(ju)001:2175: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyis bya ba thams cad sgrub
NK067(ju)001:2176: pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag pa 'gro
NK067(ju)001:2177: ba'i don mdzad pa la thogs pa med pa'i phrin
NK067(ju)001:2178: las 'jug pa bya grub ye shes te lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2179: de dag ye shes gnyis su bsdu tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:2180: zur pa rnams chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK067(ju)001:2181: phyi ma bzhi po rten brten pa'i cha nas ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes su 'adu'o //
NK067(ju)001:2185: mnyam nyid gnyis gnas lugs gzigs pa'i cha nas ji lta ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2186: gzhan gsum 'char gzhi dang yul gzigs pa dang de'i
NK067(ju)001:2187: don mdzad pa'i cha nas ji snyed pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)001:2188: so // zhes gsungs te ji ltar bshad kyang khyad par med do //
NK067(ju)001:2189: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK067(ju)001:2190: de ltar na nyon sgrib dang shes sgrib kyis bsdus
NK067(ju)001:2191: pa'i med snang blo bur gyi sgrib gnyis bag chags
NK067(ju)001:2192: snang gsum gyi dri ma dang bcas pa mtha' dag
NK067(ju)001:2193: spangs shing / ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa
NK067(ju)001:2194: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes bya'i chos thams cad
NK067(ju)001:2195: mngon sum du gzigs pa'i sgo nas spang rtogs kyi
NK067(ju)001:2196: yon tan thams cad mthar phyin zhing /
NK067(ju)001:2197: de'i mthu las gdul bya so so'i skal ba dang 'tshams par zhi ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2200: drag po la sogs te gang la gang gis ji
NK067(ju)001:2201: ltar 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi sgo mtha' yas dus
NK067(ju)001:2203: 'bad rtsol med par lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2204: nam mkha' ji srid pa de srid du rgya chen rgyun mi chad par 'byung ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2207: las ni rgyun mi chad par 'dod //
NK067(ju)001:2209: gnyis pa las gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2210: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam tshig /
NK067(ju)001:2211: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyi //
NK067(ju)001:2212: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK067(ju)001:2214: de kho na nyid lta ba /
NK067(ju)001:2220: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)001:2222: gnas su stob pa mchod pa /
NK067(ju)001:2224: dang po lta ba la gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:2227: thabs kyi lta spyod chen po ni //
NK067(ju)001:2228: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK067(ju)001:2229: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK067(ju)001:2230: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK067(ju)001:2231: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis //
NK067(ju)001:2232: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK067(ju)001:2233: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK067(ju)001:2234: zhes pas spros pa'i mtha' gang du yang ma reg pa'i cha nas dbu ma pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2235: chos thams cad sems kyi rang rtsal tsam du 'du
NK067(ju)001:2236: ba'i cha nas sems tsam pa dang phyogs mtshungs kyang
NK067(ju)001:2238: de dag las khyad par du gyur pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2239: de yang ye gdod ma nas dbyings /
NK067(ju)001:2241: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te dkor bdun
NK067(ju)001:2242: ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa lhag pa
NK067(ju)001:2244: de nyid kyi rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang ye
NK067(ju)001:2245: shes rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas 'khor
NK067(ju)001:2246: 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid du rdzogs
NK067(ju)001:2247: pa ni lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste
NK067(ju)001:2248: / de gnyis kyang phyogs su lhung ba min par
NK067(ju)001:2249: lhag pa bden gnyis zung 'jug ngo bo dbyer med
NK067(ju)001:2250: phyed par mnyam pa nyid du gnas shing /
NK067(ju)001:2251: der 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las kyang yang dag par
NK067(ju)001:2252: 'das pas na tha snyad tsam du lhag pa bden
NK067(ju)001:2253: pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba zhes ming
NK067(ju)001:2256: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK067(ju)001:2257: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa'ang //
NK067(ju)001:2258: de min zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK067(ju)001:2259: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK067(ju)001:2261: lhag pa zhes pa'i sgra yang /
NK067(ju)001:2262: khyad par du 'phags pa'i don te /
NK067(ju)001:2263: phar phyin theg pa nas don dam bden ngor 'khor
NK067(ju)001:2264: 'das mnyam nyid du bzhed pa tsam phyogs mthun kyang
NK067(ju)001:2265: / sngags lugs 'dir ni kun rdzob tu yang chos
NK067(ju)001:2266: thams cad la mi gnyis pa'i bsam brjod dang ldan
NK067(ju)001:2267: pas na rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par du 'phags
NK067(ju)001:2268: pa'i phyir de skad du brjod pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2270: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK067(ju)001:2271: don dam du ni dbyer med la //
NK067(ju)001:2272: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK067(ju)001:2273: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK067(ju)001:2274: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK067(ju)001:2275: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK067(ju)001:2276: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK067(ju)001:2277: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK067(ju)001:2281: dri shir lta ba la'o zhes pa'i byings don gyis
NK067(ju)001:2282: bsgrubs pas lta ba zhes bya ba la 'jug ste
NK067(ju)001:2283: / gnas lugs kyi don la de dang rjes su
NK067(ju)001:2284: mthun pa'i shes rab kyis gtan tshigs la sogs pa'i
NK067(ju)001:2285: sgo nas sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i don gyis na lta
NK067(ju)001:2286: / ba zhes bya'o // dbye na dbang po yang
NK067(ju)001:2287: rab la gtan tshigs kyis rtogs par bya ba ste
NK067(ju)001:2288: / ba zhes bya'o // / rgyal po dzah'i lam rnam bkod du /
NK067(ju)001:2289: de ltar tshul gsum brjod pa yis //
NK067(ju)001:2290: mthong ba gang yin shes rab spyan //
NK067(ju)001:2291: de yang mngon sum gzhan spangs te //
NK067(ju)001:2292: sgra tshig rten 'brel zhen tsam min //
NK067(ju)001:2293: yul min rang rig bden dbyer med //
NK067(ju)001:2294: blo'i gting go ba mngon sum yul //
NK067(ju)001:2296: dbang 'bring la rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i rtags la brten nas rtogs par bya ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2298: dang po rang gi rig pa yi //
NK067(ju)001:2300: phyogs dang kha dog la sogs kyis //
NK067(ju)001:2301: mtshon nas ji bzhin nyid rtogs byed //
NK067(ju)001:2305: gcig shos mthar phyin ye shes kyi //
NK067(ju)001:2306: dkyil 'khor rten dang brten can ltar //
NK067(ju)001:2308: dbang rtul la brgyud de rtogs par bya ba nye ring gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:2311: dman la rgya gsum goms pa yi //
NK067(ju)001:2312: brtan nas rtags spyad klung zhugs mthong //
NK067(ju)001:2313: bsgom pa'i lam du bstan par bya //
NK067(ju)001:2314: rim par skye la the tshom med //
NK067(ju)001:2318: de min rgyu tsam gsog byed pa //
NK067(ju)001:2319: rgyud las 'di skad gsungs pa ste //
NK067(ju)001:2320: chos nyid rten cing 'brel bris na //
NK067(ju)001:2321: chos nyid don rnams rtogs 'gyur te //
NK067(ju)001:2323: gnyis pa spyod pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:2327: rjes mthun spyod pa gzhung bzhin spyad //
NK067(ju)001:2329: gsang sngags dang rjes mthun gyi thabs shes khyad par
NK067(ju)001:2330: can gyis zin pa'i lam pa'i sgo gsum gyi bya
NK067(ju)001:2331: bar gyur pa gang yin pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2332: spyir lam gyi nyams len thams cad lta spyod gnyis su 'du na'ang /
NK067(ju)001:2333: gtso che ba'i dbang du spyi ming bye brag la
NK067(ju)001:2334: btags nas mnyam bzhag dang rjes mthun thun mtshams kyi
NK067(ju)001:2337: tsar+ya'i sgra las drangs na tsa ra spyod pa'i byings
NK067(ju)001:2338: don gyis bsgrubs pas spyod pa zhes bya ba la
NK067(ju)001:2339: 'jug ste / gang spyad bya'i yul la dus tshod
NK067(ju)001:2340: dang 'brel bas tshul bzhin du spyod par byed pa'i
NK067(ju)001:2343: spyir lus ngag yid gsum yongs su dag par bya ba yin la /
NK067(ju)001:2345: spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel bar bslab ste /
NK067(ju)001:2346: las dang po pa'i dus su gzabs shing yod pa dge sbyong gzhon nu'i spyod pa lta bu /
NK067(ju)001:2347: de las cung zad goms te mnyam rjes bsre bar
NK067(ju)001:2348: nus pa na rtogs pa rkyen thub tu byed pa
NK067(ju)001:2349: smyon pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2350: brtan pa cher thob nas rtogs pa bri gang med
NK067(ju)001:2351: par gyur pa na gzhan phan kho na la bslab
NK067(ju)001:2352: pa rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi spyod pa lta bu
NK067(ju)001:2354: bye brag tu thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2355: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa gnyis su bshad cing /
NK067(ju)001:2357: dang por lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su dad brtson gyi spyod pa spyad de /
NK067(ju)001:2361: yid ches kyi dad pa dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:2362: de lta bu'i dad pas kun nas bslang ste thos
NK067(ju)001:2363: bsam la zhugs nas brtson 'grus thang lhod med pas
NK067(ju)001:2364: de don mthar phyin par spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2365: gnyis pa stong chen gyi dus su shes rab dang mthun pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2366: mnyam gzhag tu stong chen rnam par mi rtog pa'i 'od gsal bsgom zhing /
NK067(ju)001:2367: rjes thob rjes shes kyi gnas skabs su yang de'i ngang lam mi g.yo bar spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2370: spyod dgu dor ba'i gcig car spang //
NK067(ju)001:2371: mi dmigs mthun par spyod ces bya //
NK067(ju)001:2373: gsum pa snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su thabs dang mthun pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2374: mnyam gzhag tu dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje rtsol
NK067(ju)001:2375: med shugs 'byung du 'char ba la bslab cing rjes
NK067(ju)001:2376: thob rjes shes la'ang de'i ngang bskyang ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:2379: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK067(ju)001:2380: srid gsum sgyu ma 'dra bar ni //
NK067(ju)001:2382: bzhi pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su phyogs gcig
NK067(ju)001:2383: pa ste mnyam rjes gnyis kar zung 'jug phyag rgya
NK067(ju)001:2384: gcig pa'i rnal 'byor kho na la spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2386: rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor bar skabs su //
NK067(ju)001:2387: chos spyod dgu yi spros pa dor //
NK067(ju)001:2388: rgyud la ldan yang blang bya min //
NK067(ju)001:2389: mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin phyir ro //
NK067(ju)001:2391: lnga pa phyag rgya spros bcas kyi skabs su spros pa dang bcas pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2392: mnyam rjes gnyis kar spyod yul thams cad lha'i rol mor 'char ba la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2395: spyod yul mthong thos thams cad kun //
NK067(ju)001:2398: ma nyams de yi dbyings na gnas //
NK067(ju)001:2399: shes rab mchog gis rtag tu spyad //
NK067(ju)001:2401: drug pa tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su tshogs kyi spyod pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2402: mnyam rjes gnyis kar yo byad lnga la chags med du spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2405: spyod lam yo byad lnga spyod cing //
NK067(ju)001:2406: dngos su mchod pa rnam gnyis so //
NK067(ju)001:2408: bdun pa zag med slob ma'i lam rig 'dzin bzhi'i skabs su rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2409: bdag don du rang sa'i dri ma phra ba rnams
NK067(ju)001:2410: sbyong zhing gzhan don rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pas sprul
NK067(ju)001:2411: pa ma 'gags par ston cing gdul bya'i don mdzad
NK067(ju)001:2412: pa'o // de yang snga ma las /
NK067(ju)001:2413: dkyil 'khor rol pa'i tshul spyod pas //
NK067(ju)001:2414: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa bdag gi don //
NK067(ju)001:2415: smin pas phrin las rdzogs byed pa //
NK067(ju)001:2418: dkyus sar phyin pa'i cang shes bzhin //
NK067(ju)001:2419: kun tu 'gro ba bdag po'i don //
NK067(ju)001:2420: rdzu 'phrul chos snang rjes ston brjod //
NK067(ju)001:2422: mnyam bzhag ngang las ma g.yos bzhin /
NK067(ju)001:2423: stong gi 'jig rten brgya stong phrag /
NK067(ju)001:2424: bcu yi rdul snyed 'jig rten dang //
NK067(ju)001:2425: zhing grangs med pa brgya stong phrag /
NK067(ju)001:2426: bcu yi rdul snyed zhing khams su //
NK067(ju)001:2427: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK067(ju)001:2428: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK067(ju)001:2430: nyid phyir rdo rje 'dzin rdzogs la //
NK067(ju)001:2432: gsang ba'i tan+t+ra ston pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:2433: de bzhin bsdu ba mdzad pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:2434: zhes pas lhun grub rig 'dzin te de ltar rig 'dzin gyi spyod pa rnams gsungs so //
NK067(ju)001:2435: de ltar rim gyis pa'i spyod pa bdun bshad nas /
NK067(ju)001:2436: gcig car ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2437: chos thams cad la blang dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2439: mi dmigs pa las rnam par spyod //
NK067(ju)001:2440: de ltar spyod pa kun spyod kyang //
NK067(ju)001:2441: dam pa'i don de spyod mchog nyid //
NK067(ju)001:2443: gsum pa dkyil 'khor la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:2446: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK067(ju)001:2447: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK067(ju)001:2448: zhes pas bkod pa lha'i 'khor lo rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:2453: yang gsang ltar 'god pa dang bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)001:2455: man+da la'i sgra las drangs na /
NK067(ju)001:2456: man+da ni snying po'am bcud dang /
NK067(ju)001:2457: la ni 'dzin pa'am len pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2458: snying po'i yon tan gyi gzhi 'dzin pas na snying po len pa zhes dang /
NK067(ju)001:2459: yang man+da la zhes pa'i man+da dang la so sor
NK067(ju)001:2460: ma phye bar sgra gzugs po zlum po'am bskor ba'i
NK067(ju)001:2461: don la 'jug pas na gang gtso bo la 'khor
NK067(ju)001:2462: gyis bskor ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor ro //
NK067(ju)001:2464: sangs rgyas gsang bas chos don du /
NK067(ju)001:2465: dbye ba rang bzhin ting 'dzin dang //
NK067(ju)001:2466: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum //
NK067(ju)001:2470: sku gsung thugs kyi dbye ba las //
NK067(ju)001:2472: zhes gsum du dbye ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2474: dkyil 'khor rnam pa bcu gnyis te //
NK067(ju)001:2475: de bzhin nyid dang rang bzhin dang //
NK067(ju)001:2477: ting nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2478: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2479: byang chub sems dang lhag byang sems //
NK067(ju)001:2480: tshogs dang lhun grub dkyil 'khor ro //
NK067(ju)001:2481: zhes bcu gnyis su dbye ba sogs yod pa las /
NK067(ju)001:2484: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK067(ju)001:2486: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK067(ju)001:2487: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdun du phye nas bshad de /
NK067(ju)001:2488: dang po rang bzhin dkyil 'khor la /
NK067(ju)001:2489: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)001:2490: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:2492: chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK067(ju)001:2494: chos nyid rang bzhin spros bral te /
NK067(ju)001:2495: dngos po kun kyang de bzhin pas //
NK067(ju)001:2496: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK067(ju)001:2499: rang gi ye shes mngon sum du gyur pas 'og
NK067(ju)001:2500: min chos kyi dbyings su sku dang ye shes 'du
NK067(ju)001:2501: 'bral med pa'i dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2504: bzhugs pa dkyil dang 'khor gyi tshul //
NK067(ju)001:2506: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2507: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du rang shar ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2509: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK067(ju)001:2510: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK067(ju)001:2511: so so'i mtshan nyid shes rab rtogs //
NK067(ju)001:2512: gnyis med 'brel ba thabs chen yin //
NK067(ju)001:2514: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2516: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK067(ju)001:2517: tshon dang bri dang rnam pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:2518: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK067(ju)001:2519: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK067(ju)001:2521: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2523: gzhi dang rang mtshan blang dbang dang //
NK067(ju)001:2524: sbyang byin bsrung dang bzung ba ni //
NK067(ju)001:2525: dang po'i nying lag nyid du bshad //
NK067(ju)001:2529: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK067(ju)001:2530: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK067(ju)001:2531: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK067(ju)001:2533: yang na khru ni bcu drug gam //
NK067(ju)001:2534: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lngar bya //
NK067(ju)001:2535: zhes lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dngos bshad nas /
NK067(ju)001:2536: zhar byung lhag ting gi tshad ni /
NK067(ju)001:2537: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK067(ju)001:2538: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK067(ju)001:2539: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor sna tshogs bsgom //
NK067(ju)001:2543: rig pas thig ni gdab bar bya //
NK067(ju)001:2545: phur bu srad bu tshon phye dang //
NK067(ju)001:2546: gos rgyan mdzes pa'i yod 'ong grogs //
NK067(ju)001:2547: thig gdab cho ga phun sum tshogs //
NK067(ju)001:2548: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK067(ju)001:2552: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK067(ju)001:2554: ma mthong rmongs la bstan phyir dang //
NK067(ju)001:2555: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am //
NK067(ju)001:2556: lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK067(ju)001:2557: 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK067(ju)001:2560: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK067(ju)001:2561: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK067(ju)001:2562: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:2563: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK067(ju)001:2564: zhes pa ltar dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang gis 'dul pa'i cho ga bzhin du bri'o //
NK067(ju)001:2565: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2566: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK067(ju)001:2568: yang na gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar te /
NK067(ju)001:2570: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK067(ju)001:2571: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK067(ju)001:2572: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK067(ju)001:2575: nub gnyis pa'i las rim spyir bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2576: skabs thob kyi las rim dkyil 'khor rab gnas so //
NK067(ju)001:2582: thig tshon rab gnas rnams dang /
NK067(ju)001:2586: lha sta gon gsum gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:2588: las khrigs rnam pa dgu la sogs pa'i sgo nas bya ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2590: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK067(ju)001:2592: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK067(ju)001:2593: zhes sogs 'khrugs sdebs kyi sgo nas bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:2595: skabs thob kyi dbang gis las bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:2597: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK067(ju)001:2598: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK067(ju)001:2599: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK067(ju)001:2600: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK067(ju)001:2602: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2603: sgrub mchod la sogs pa sngon du 'gro ba'i sgo
NK067(ju)001:2604: nas dang por slob dpon rang nyid zhugs rjes slob
NK067(ju)001:2605: ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2607: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK067(ju)001:2608: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK067(ju)001:2611: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK067(ju)001:2612: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK067(ju)001:2613: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK067(ju)001:2614: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2615: sgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK067(ju)001:2616: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2617: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2618: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK067(ju)001:2621: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK067(ju)001:2622: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK067(ju)001:2623: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK067(ju)001:2624: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK067(ju)001:2628: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK067(ju)001:2629: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yis //
NK067(ju)001:2630: bsod nams brtag pa gang yin pa /
NK067(ju)001:2631: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:2633: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2634: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK067(ju)001:2635: yul du byas nas rang rig ma bcos pa'i don
NK067(ju)001:2636: la rnam par bzhag pas rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK067(ju)001:2637: rang rtsal ye shes lngar 'gag pa med par 'char
NK067(ju)001:2639: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK067(ju)001:2640: zhes sogs sho lo ka gcig dang /
NK067(ju)001:2643: thams cad dbyings su bsdus nas ni //
NK067(ju)001:2644: nyid kyi thugs la thim byas te //
NK067(ju)001:2645: thams cad chos sku'i phyag rgya che //
NK067(ju)001:2647: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2649: lhag pa ting 'dzin rnam pa gnyis //
NK067(ju)001:2650: gdul ba'i don phyir zhi khro ste //
NK067(ju)001:2652: thugs rje zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)001:2653: bdud 'dul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:2654: zhi khro gnyis ka la mtshungs par /
NK067(ju)001:2655: sngon 'gro las bdun sngon du 'gro bas /
NK067(ju)001:2660: bdag dang mtha' yas sogs kyis khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed /
NK067(ju)001:2661: chos thams cad stong nyid de bzhin nyid du bsgom pa de ting /
NK067(ju)001:2662: de ma rtogs pa rnams la dmigs med kyi snying rje bsgom pa kun ting /
NK067(ju)001:2663: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i rang rtsal
NK067(ju)001:2664: rgyu'i yi ge a dkar por bsgom pa rgyu ting
NK067(ju)001:2665: dang / de las yi ge phra mo'i 'phro 'du la sems sbyangs nas /
NK067(ju)001:2666: 'byung lnga'i zhen rtog sbyang phyir dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2667: ma dag pa snod kyi zhen pa sbyong phyir sa bon b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang dang /
NK067(ju)001:2668: de'i nang du bcud kyi zhen rtog sbyang phyir bdag sras gzhan sras sam /
NK067(ju)001:2669: cho ga gsum bskyed lta bus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)001:2670: gsal btab pa la rang rigs kyis dbang bskur zhing
NK067(ju)001:2671: / sku gsung thugs rdo rjer byin gyis brlab pa rnams bya ste /
NK067(ju)001:2672: de'i mthar snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drang ba /
NK067(ju)001:2673: me tog dor zhing dbyer med du bstim pa /
NK067(ju)001:2674: phyag mchod bshad pa bya ba /
NK067(ju)001:2675: dngos grub gsol zhing dam bca' ba /
NK067(ju)001:2676: dzapa khang phye nas 'phro 'du gsum gsal bas dzapa bzlas skabs kyi mjug bsdu dang bcas bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:2678: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis zhes sogs kyis khyad par gyi
NK067(ju)001:2679: sbyor ba ting nge 'dzin gyi dgos ched bstan pa
NK067(ju)001:2680: sngon du 'gro bas de ting dang /
NK067(ju)001:2681: kun ting gnyis kyi mthar rang rig h+aum las cho
NK067(ju)001:2682: ga gsum gyis rgyu'i he ru kar bskyed pa rgyu
NK067(ju)001:2683: ting ste ting 'dzin rnam gsum dang /
NK067(ju)001:2684: de'i thugs ka nas sa bon spros te 'byung ba rim brtsegs gzhal yas khang /
NK067(ju)001:2685: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor dang bcas bskyed tshul cho
NK067(ju)001:2686: ga gnyis lta bus zhi ba dang 'dra bar bsgom
NK067(ju)001:2689: snyan gsan dbab pa sogs las kyi rim pa'i ting
NK067(ju)001:2690: nge 'dzin rnams zhi ba dang phyogs mtshungs par bya
NK067(ju)001:2691: ba'o // mjug gi cho ga ni /
NK067(ju)001:2692: go bgo lus bsrung gi bar don lngas bstan pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)001:2693: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2695: byang sems phyi nang gsang ba yang //
NK067(ju)001:2696: gnas bzhi khams gsum ye shes che //
NK067(ju)001:2698: phyi byang chub kyi sems rtsa dang rlung /
NK067(ju)001:2699: nang byang chub kyi sems thig le /
NK067(ju)001:2700: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye shes dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:2702: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK067(ju)001:2703: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK067(ju)001:2704: srog shing gsum dang 'khor lo bzhi //
NK067(ju)001:2707: sbyang gzhi ye shes kyi rlung dang /
NK067(ju)001:2708: sbyang bya las kyi rlung gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:2709: phyi ma la rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i rlung bcu /
NK067(ju)001:2710: snar rgyu ba'i rlung dang bcas pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2712: snying ga na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le sogs ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK067(ju)001:2713: rnam shes kyi thig le dwangs snyigs la sogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2715: steng 'og gi sgo la brten nas bde chen gyi ye shes bskyed pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2717: dkyil ni snying po zhes brjod de //
NK067(ju)001:2718: byang chub sems ni bde chen po //
NK067(ju)001:2719: len par byed pas dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK067(ju)001:2722: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)001:2723: zhi khro gnyis ka la tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:2725: tshogs ni 'byor pa rnam pa gsum //
NK067(ju)001:2726: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2728: bzhi pa dbang la'ang gsum ste ngo bo ni /
NK067(ju)001:2730: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag snyad //
NK067(ju)001:2731: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK067(ju)001:2732: ngo bo nyid ces rnam pa bshad //
NK067(ju)001:2733: ces pas spyir dbang la rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)001:2736: dbang gi rgyu gdod ma nas rang la rang chas su bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2738: dbang rdzas rab gnas kyis byin gyis rlobs pa can no //
NK067(ju)001:2739: gnyis pa la rgyu'i rkyen no //
NK067(ju)001:2740: phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur du rung ba'i snod ldan gyi slob ma'o //
NK067(ju)001:2742: dbang gsum bskur nus pa'i rdo rje slob dpon tshad ldan no //
NK067(ju)001:2744: rdzas sngags ting 'dzin gsum 'dzom pa'i nus pa khyad par can no //
NK067(ju)001:2746: dbang snga mas go phye nas phyi ma 'byung ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:2747: de ltar rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:2748: drug po tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi
NK067(ju)001:2749: chos dbang gi ye shes rgyud la 'jog pa'i las
NK067(ju)001:2750: kyis thar pa'i myu gu mngon du bskyed pa'am skye
NK067(ju)001:2751: nges kyi nus rung du smin par byed pa ni
NK067(ju)001:2754: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK067(ju)001:2756: shiny+tsa ni gtor ba'am blugs pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2757: dbang gis sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud pa'i cha nas mngon par gtor ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2758: 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus pa khyad par can
NK067(ju)001:2759: rgyud la 'jog pa'i cha nas mngon par blugs pa'i
NK067(ju)001:2764: 'bras bu'i dbang gsum du 'gyur ba las /
NK067(ju)001:2767: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK067(ju)001:2768: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK067(ju)001:2769: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK067(ju)001:2770: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK067(ju)001:2773: dad dang brtson 'grus gsum ldan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2774: brtul zhugs gsum ldan slob ma la //
NK067(ju)001:2775: zhes pas gang zag rim gnyis kyi lam nyams su
NK067(ju)001:2776: len par mi nus na yang dad pa can la
NK067(ju)001:2777: phan dbang tsam bskur ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:2778: de'i steng du nus dbang lnga las /
NK067(ju)001:2779: rgyud la thos bsam byed nus kyi gang zag la nyan dbang /
NK067(ju)001:2780: bskyed rim gyi lam rnams dang rdzogs rim rjes mthun
NK067(ju)001:2781: tsam nyams su len nus la sgom dbang ste bdag
NK067(ju)001:2782: don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can dang /
NK067(ju)001:2783: de'i steng du zhi rgyas sogs phrin las kyi sbyor
NK067(ju)001:2784: bas gzhan don byed nus la phrin las kyi dbang
NK067(ju)001:2785: dang / rgyud 'chad nus la 'chad dbang ste gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can dang /
NK067(ju)001:2786: de'i steng du rab gnas dang slob ma la dbang
NK067(ju)001:2787: bskur ba sogs rdo rje slob dpon mchog tu 'os
NK067(ju)001:2788: pa rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don nus pa rnams la
NK067(ju)001:2789: bdag po'i dbang ste nus dbang lnga /
NK067(ju)001:2790: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba
NK067(ju)001:2791: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba lta bu ste spyir
NK067(ju)001:2794: khyad par can gyi lam 'di sogs la sngon du
NK067(ju)001:2795: ma zhugs pa gcig dang por dkyil 'khor du bcug
NK067(ju)001:2796: nas dbang gis smin par byed pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2798: sngon du dbang thob bskyed rdzogs gang rung gi lam
NK067(ju)001:2799: nyams su len ba zhin pa'i gang zag lta bu
NK067(ju)001:2801: de'i rgyud kyi sngags sdom je dag je bzang du
NK067(ju)001:2802: 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i ched du bla ma rdo
NK067(ju)001:2803: rje slob dpon gyi dkyil 'khor du bcug ste dbang
NK067(ju)001:2804: bskur ba'am / rang nyid kyis bdag 'jug byed pa lta bu ni lam dbang ste /
NK067(ju)001:2805: don du na theg pa mchog gi lam la bgrod
NK067(ju)001:2806: bzhin pa'i gang zag gis bla ma'i bdag 'jug gang
NK067(ju)001:2809: pha rol du phyin pa'i lam gyis bsgrub pa'i mi slob lam dang /
NK067(ju)001:2810: sngags rang lugs kyi mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi sa la bzhugs pa'i gang zag rnams la /
NK067(ju)001:2811: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang chen por /
NK067(ju)001:2812: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa rigs drug pa dpal
NK067(ju)001:2813: kun tu bzang pos nang gi mngon byang la brten
NK067(ju)001:2814: nas gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas shes
NK067(ju)001:2815: sgrib phra ba snang gsum gyi dri ma sbyang nas
NK067(ju)001:2816: rang gi ye shes ji lta ba mngon du byed
NK067(ju)001:2817: pa'i sgo nas ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du
NK067(ju)001:2820: ston pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis rgyun mtha'i byang sems la 'og min du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:2823: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK067(ju)001:2824: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:2826: de las kyang bum dbang la phan nus gnyis su phye bas lngar 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)001:2828: dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK067(ju)001:2829: gnyis pa nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:2830: gsum pa nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:2831: bzhi pas de nyid brtan par byed //
NK067(ju)001:2832: lnga pas brtan pa nyams lon pas //
NK067(ju)001:2835: dang po phan dbang gi snod rung du smin par
NK067(ju)001:2836: byed pa'i sgo nas 'di phyi gang rung du bskyed
NK067(ju)001:2837: rdzogs kyi lam la 'jug pa'i skal ldan du byed
NK067(ju)001:2838: pa'i sa bon gsos 'debs pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2839: gnyis pa nus dbang gis da lta nas rang gzhan gyi don byed pa'i nus pa bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2840: gsum pa gsang dbang gi bde chen khyad par du byas pa'i nyams myong bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:2841: bzhi pa ye shes rang gnas kyis khams 'dzin grems
NK067(ju)001:2842: la sogs pa'i sgo nas de nyid brtan par byed
NK067(ju)001:2843: pa dang / lnga pa bde ba chen pos brtan
NK067(ju)001:2844: pa de'i don nyams su len te rang bzhin lhan
NK067(ju)001:2845: cig skyes pa'i ye shes su la bzla bar byed
NK067(ju)001:2846: pa dang / pa'o // de yang zhi ba phan dbang bcu /
NK067(ju)001:2848: zab dbang gsum ste bco brgyad /
NK067(ju)001:2849: de la phan dbang bcu ni /
NK067(ju)001:2851: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2852: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK067(ju)001:2853: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK067(ju)001:2854: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK067(ju)001:2861: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams te lnga'o //
NK067(ju)001:2865: bde ba chen po'i dbang dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:2867: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK067(ju)001:2868: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco nga ste //
NK067(ju)001:2869: zhes pa ltar phan dbang la nyer brgyad du phye bas sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK067(ju)001:2871: bsgyur ba lnga la sum cu drug /
NK067(ju)001:2873: lnga pa dam tshig la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:2876: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK067(ju)001:2877: rmi lam du'ang dam tshig brjod //
NK067(ju)001:2878: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK067(ju)001:2879: ces pas gang bsrung bya'i don khyad par can ni
NK067(ju)001:2880: 'og tu 'byung ba'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK067(ju)001:2882: de dag las nam yang mi 'da' bar sdom par byed pa'i sems dpa' rgyun chags dang /
NK067(ju)001:2883: gnyid dang sems yengs pa la sogs pa'i gnas skabs
NK067(ju)001:2884: su yang tshig sdom pa'i sa bon dang bcas pa'o
NK067(ju)001:2886: sa ma ya'i sgra las drangs na /
NK067(ju)001:2887: sa ma ya ni dngos su yal gam bcas pa'i tha tshig la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)001:2888: sngon rang gis ji ltar dam bcas pa las 'da' bar bya ba min pa'i phyir dam tshig go //
NK067(ju)001:2891: dam pa sku gsung thugs yin te //
NK067(ju)001:2896: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:2897: spro na sum brgya drug cur dbye ba dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)001:2900: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK067(ju)001:2901: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK067(ju)001:2902: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK067(ju)001:2903: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK067(ju)001:2904: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te /
NK067(ju)001:2905: sgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)001:2907: dang po bla med mi spang ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:2908: yul bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems lhag pa bden gnyis mi spang ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:2910: lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med du rtogs nas sgo
NK067(ju)001:2911: gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi
NK067(ju)001:2914: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK067(ju)001:2915: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK067(ju)001:2916: snang stong gnyis med rdo rje'i sku //
NK067(ju)001:2917: byas mthong zos pa thams cad kyang //
NK067(ju)001:2918: sems phyir gang yang byas snang med //
NK067(ju)001:2919: dran dang shes bzhin sngon btang la //
NK067(ju)001:2920: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK067(ju)001:2921: theg chen sngags par ci yis chud //
NK067(ju)001:2923: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:2925: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK067(ju)001:2926: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK067(ju)001:2927: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /
NK067(ju)001:2928: zhes pa ltar slob dpon drug po bkur thabs drug gi sgo nas bkur te /
NK067(ju)001:2930: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK067(ju)001:2931: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK067(ju)001:2932: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul bstan te //
NK067(ju)001:2937: man ngag nod pa gsum ni lhag par yang bkur ba'i yul te /
NK067(ju)001:2939: rgyud 'grol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK067(ju)001:2941: gsum pa sngags rgya rgyun mi bcad pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2942: yul sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:2943: de dag nyams su len tshul ni /
NK067(ju)001:2945: rab kyi chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam //
NK067(ju)001:2946: nyid gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK067(ju)001:2947: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK067(ju)001:2948: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK067(ju)001:2949: dus bzhi'i bar du mi bcad cing //
NK067(ju)001:2950: tha ma bya ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK067(ju)001:2951: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK067(ju)001:2952: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed pa //
NK067(ju)001:2953: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK067(ju)001:2954: tshogs dang gtor ma'am de bzhin du //
NK067(ju)001:2957: bzhi pa mched la byams pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2959: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK067(ju)001:2960: gang yang bdag las gzhan min dang //
NK067(ju)001:2961: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK067(ju)001:2962: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin ni //
NK067(ju)001:2963: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK067(ju)001:2964: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK067(ju)001:2965: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK067(ju)001:2966: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK067(ju)001:2968: des mtshon pa'i rdo rje'i mched rnams dang byang chub
NK067(ju)001:2969: bar du mi 'bral ba'i lhag bsam rgyun mi 'chad
NK067(ju)001:2970: par byed pa'o // lnga pa gsang ba mi smra ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:2972: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:2973: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK067(ju)001:2975: zhes gang la gsang bya'i yul bstan nas //
NK067(ju)001:2978: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK067(ju)001:2979: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK067(ju)001:2984: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa rnams so //
NK067(ju)001:2986: spyi gsang bzhi las lta zab ni theg dman sogs blo 'phangs dma' ba rnams dang /
NK067(ju)001:2987: spyod pa ni ma 'dres pa thams cad la gsang /
NK067(ju)001:2988: yi dam gyi lha sngags dang grub rtags ni ma 'dres pa la bstan na dam tshig nyams shing /
NK067(ju)001:2989: 'dres pa la bstan na yang dngos grub nyams par 'gyur bas gsang bar bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:2991: sgrub pa ji tsam byed pa'i bar de nyid du gsang ngo //
NK067(ju)001:2993: gang mthong ba las ma dad par 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i cha thams cad do //
NK067(ju)001:2994: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:2995: slob dpon dang mched kyis gsang bar gdams pa rnams so //
NK067(ju)001:2996: gnyis pa la mi spang pa lnga dang /
NK067(ju)001:3000: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK067(ju)001:3001: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK067(ju)001:3002: zhes pa ltar lnga yin la /
NK067(ju)001:3003: de la dbye na bsal bkra las /
NK067(ju)001:3004: mi spang dam tshig bshad bya ba //
NK067(ju)001:3005: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK067(ju)001:3006: zhes yang log gnyis gnyis so //
NK067(ju)001:3008: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK067(ju)001:3009: dag pa'i snod chu mi 'dor ro //
NK067(ju)001:3013: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK067(ju)001:3014: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK067(ju)001:3015: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la //
NK067(ju)001:3016: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK067(ju)001:3017: zhes pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po re re
NK067(ju)001:3018: la thabs shes gnyis gnyis su phye bas bcu dang
NK067(ju)001:3019: / yang rtsa ba lnga po re re la sum cu rer phye bas chig brgya lnga bcu ste /
NK067(ju)001:3020: sngar gyi bcu dang bsdoms pas brgya drug cu'o //
NK067(ju)001:3021: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu po re re la nyi shu nyi shur phye bas nyis brgya ste /
NK067(ju)001:3022: sngar gyi brgya drug cu dang sdom pas sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK067(ju)001:3023: de dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas par phra rgyas las shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:3024: drug pa phrin las la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:3027: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK067(ju)001:3029: sems can thams cad rang gi pha mar shes pa'i byams pa /
NK067(ju)001:3030: de dag rigs drug gi gnas sdug bsngal gyi yo lang la spyod pa snying rje /
NK067(ju)001:3031: sems can 'ga' zhig lha mi'i 'dod yon gyis 'byor pa sogs bde bar gnas pa la dga' ba /
NK067(ju)001:3032: nye ring chags sdang dang bral ba'i btang snyoms te /
NK067(ju)001:3033: de lta bu'i tshad med pa bzhi'i rgyu las byung ba'i byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK067(ju)001:3034: 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis zin pa'i
NK067(ju)001:3035: sgo nas gtso bor gzhan don sgrub pa la dmigs
NK067(ju)001:3036: pa'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad spyod do //
NK067(ju)001:3038: karma zhes pa'i sgra las lus ngag yid gsum ste
NK067(ju)001:3039: sgo gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bya ba'i mtshan nyid can
NK067(ju)001:3040: ni las de byed pa po'i 'dod pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:3043: zhi ba la sogs rab dbye bas //
NK067(ju)001:3044: las ni rnam pa bzhir bsdus so //
NK067(ju)001:3045: zhes pas nad gdon sogs mi mthun phyogs zhi ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:3046: tshe dpal sogs mthun phyogs rgyas pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3047: log lta can dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:3048: gdug pa can tshar gcod pa drag po'i phrin las te bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)001:3049: de dag kyang gang gis bya ba'i thabs kyi rim pa ni /
NK067(ju)001:3054: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba rnams te /
NK067(ju)001:3056: bdag gzhan don sgrub phrin las ni //
NK067(ju)001:3057: mchod rten phyag rgya'i sgo dang ni //
NK067(ju)001:3058: hom bro glu dang rdzas kyis bya //
NK067(ju)001:3060: de la me'i sgo nas las bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:3062: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK067(ju)001:3063: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK067(ju)001:3064: phur bu lha dus las rim dang //
NK067(ju)001:3065: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK067(ju)001:3066: zhes pa ltar las bzhi ka la don tshan bcu gcig gi sgo nas ston cing /
NK067(ju)001:3068: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa la //
NK067(ju)001:3069: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK067(ju)001:3070: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK067(ju)001:3071: zhes sogs phrin las bzhi so so la me'i sgo
NK067(ju)001:3072: nas las bya tshul phan yon dang bcas bstan no
NK067(ju)001:3073: // gnyis pa rdzas kyi sgo nas las bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:3077: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:3078: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la /
NK067(ju)001:3079: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK067(ju)001:3080: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK067(ju)001:3081: rdul du byas nas tshogs la dbul //
NK067(ju)001:3083: gsum pa lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas las bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:3084: bro'i sgo nas phrin las bzhi sgrub pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:3085: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK067(ju)001:3086: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK067(ju)001:3087: bcings gyur spyod nas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK067(ju)001:3088: myos nas gas te tshig par 'gyur //
NK067(ju)001:3089: zhes pa la sogs pas phrin las bzhi so so'i phan yon dang bcas pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3090: khro bo sgrub pa'i las kyi gtso bo ni 'di yin no //
NK067(ju)001:3091: zhes sogs kyis spyir bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:3092: bzhi pa mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)001:3093: bdag nyid zhi ba'i las la rnam snang /
NK067(ju)001:3096: drag po la badz+ra he ru kar bskyar nas rigs
NK067(ju)001:3097: so so'i sngags kyis mchod rten dkar po zlum po
NK067(ju)001:3098: sogs las mthun du btab pa'i bum nang du /
NK067(ju)001:3100: de'i 'od kyis bsgrub bya gang yin bkug nas mchod rten gyi 'og tu gnas pa la /
NK067(ju)001:3101: 'od des reg pas zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las gang yin 'grub par bsam pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:3103: drag po gtum po 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK067(ju)001:3104: bdag nyid drag por bsgoms nas ni //
NK067(ju)001:3106: bgegs kyi lid+ga mnan par bya //
NK067(ju)001:3108: de ltar sa la dngos su 'debs pa'am /
NK067(ju)001:3109: ting nge 'dzin gyis 'byung ba gzhan la 'debs pa'ang rung ste /
NK067(ju)001:3111: mchod rten 'byung ba gang la 'debs kyang /
NK067(ju)001:3113: 'jim pa la dngos su mi 'dod pa'ang min te /
NK067(ju)001:3115: yang na rgyud phyi ma las gsungs pa bzhin dngos
NK067(ju)001:3116: su bzhengs nas thab khung du byas te las bzhi'i
NK067(ju)001:3117: sbyin sreg bya bar yang bshad do //
NK067(ju)001:3118: lnga pa phyag rgya'i sgo nas las bya ba la /
NK067(ju)001:3119: phyag rgya bca' ba'i sgo nas dang /
NK067(ju)001:3120: bsgyur ba'i sgo nas las bya ba'o //
NK067(ju)001:3121: dang po ni dpal he ru ka'i las bzhi'i phyag rgya bca' ba ste /
NK067(ju)001:3123: yan lag snying po rtse gcig dang //
NK067(ju)001:3124: rtse lnga rtse dgu bcu gcig tu //
NK067(ju)001:3125: las rnams so sor rab tu sgom //
NK067(ju)001:3129: rdo rje lan gsum gsor ba yis //
NK067(ju)001:3130: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK067(ju)001:3132: zhes kun bzang yab yum khros pa'i skur bskyed la /
NK067(ju)001:3133: gzungs ma dam can dbang du bya ba dang /
NK067(ju)001:3134: de bzhin du rigs kyi he ru ka bzhir bskyed
NK067(ju)001:3135: nas so so'i phyag rgya bsgyur bas las bzhi sgrub
NK067(ju)001:3136: pa'o // bdun pa sgrub pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:3138: rgyud phyi ma kha che 'gyur las /
NK067(ju)001:3139: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK067(ju)001:3140: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas thob //
NK067(ju)001:3142: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas so //
NK067(ju)001:3143: zhes pa ltar thabs khyad par can bskyed rim gyis bsgrub bya thun mong dang /
NK067(ju)001:3144: thabs khyad par can rdzogs rim gyis bsgrub bya mchog gi dngos grub ste /
NK067(ju)001:3145: de ltar mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub rnam
NK067(ju)001:3146: pa gnyis las gang 'dod don du gnyer ba zhig
NK067(ju)001:3148: sid+d+hi'i sgra las drangs na dngos grub ste bsgrub bya dang /
NK067(ju)001:3151: 'dod pa'i don len cing thob par byed pa'am sgrub par byed pas na sgrub pa zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)001:3156: bshad rgyud rgyas pa'i le'u so sos bstan tshul gyis spyir bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3157: de dag rtsa gzhung gi bshad tshul dang sbyar te bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:3160: ro la'angsa tshe dang pra sgrub dang //
NK067(ju)001:3161: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK067(ju)001:3162: gdug pa glu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK067(ju)001:3163: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK067(ju)001:3164: yul khams lce spyang rkang mgyogs bskrad //
NK067(ju)001:3165: mi snang gzugs sgrub lha klu mo //
NK067(ju)001:3166: rgyal blon dmag dpon zhang blon sgrub //
NK067(ju)001:3169: ro langs te rdo rje zhing chen sgrub pa le'u bdun cu pa /
NK067(ju)001:3170: tshe sgrub pa zhi khro gnyis sogs cho ga dang
NK067(ju)001:3171: bcas pa'i sgo nas sgrub tshul drug cu re bzhi
NK067(ju)001:3172: pa / pra se na dbab pa le'u drug cu re lnga pa /
NK067(ju)001:3173: lha chen po ma h+aa de wa sgrub pa dang
NK067(ju)001:3174: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi sgrub pa drug cu
NK067(ju)001:3175: re drug pa / gnod byed gdug pa'i klu gdon 'dul ba bzhi bcu zhe drug pa /
NK067(ju)001:3176: rgyal po dang blon po'i chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis bzhi bcu zhe lnga pa /
NK067(ju)001:3177: yul khams dbang du bya ba sum cu so brgyad pa /
NK067(ju)001:3178: lce spyang zhes bya ba rdo rje rigs kyi rkang
NK067(ju)001:3179: mgyogs bye brag tu ston pa bzhi bcu zhe gcig
NK067(ju)001:3180: pa / rkang mgyogs kyi dngos grub spyir sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3181: dgra bgegs sogs yul gzhan du bskrad pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3182: mi snang ba'i gzugs sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3183: lha mo dang klu mo phyag rgyar 'gug cing dbang du bya ba rnams sum cu so brgyad pa /
NK067(ju)001:3184: rgyal po dang blon po sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)001:3185: dmag dpon mthu chen dang zhang blon sgrub pa rnams bzhi bcu zhe gcig pa rnams kyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:3186: las de rnams kyis rang 'bras mchog gi 'bras bu
NK067(ju)001:3187: mngon du byed mi nus pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis tshe
NK067(ju)001:3188: 'di'i ched phyir 'jig rten pa zhes thun mong gi
NK067(ju)001:3191: yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub drug /
NK067(ju)001:3196: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK067(ju)001:3197: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK067(ju)001:3200: zas dug can la yi ge bkod de 'ju 'dul
NK067(ju)001:3201: gyi las kyis sman mchog bdud rtsir 'gyur ba la
NK067(ju)001:3202: sogs pa yi ge'i 'phro 'dus nad zhi ba sogs
NK067(ju)001:3205: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK067(ju)001:3209: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK067(ju)001:3210: zhes pas nam mkha' la h'u zhes rdo rje'i skas
NK067(ju)001:3211: bsam na mngon sum du 'byung ba la sogs pa
NK067(ju)001:3212: dang / gzhan yang 'byung ba la thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul ston par nus pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:3213: rgyas pa'i so brgyad pa las /
NK067(ju)001:3214: mi gnas nam mkha'i mtha' klas par //
NK067(ju)001:3216: chu la sa bzhin 'gro ba dang //
NK067(ju)001:3217: bsreg bya 'bar ba'i dbus gnas dang //
NK067(ju)001:3218: tshangs pa'i rlung gis btegs nas kyang //
NK067(ju)001:3219: phyogs bcu kun tu phyin par 'gyur //
NK067(ju)001:3222: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang grol //
NK067(ju)001:3223: gso dang bsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK067(ju)001:3226: gnyis pa mchog gi sgrub pa la /
NK067(ju)001:3229: mchog gi dngos grub spyir bshad pa gnyis /
NK067(ju)001:3232: yi ge sgyu 'phrul tshogs sgrub dang //
NK067(ju)001:3233: rdo rje sems dang sman sgrub dang //
NK067(ju)001:3234: rigs lnga sgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK067(ju)001:3235: byin dbab bsgrub pa rnams gnyis so //
NK067(ju)001:3237: yi ge sgyu 'phrul ni rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi le'u bzhi pa la sogs pas bstan /
NK067(ju)001:3238: tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa de'i le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa la sogs pas bstan /
NK067(ju)001:3239: rgyas pa'i le'u nyer gnyis par rdor sems phyag rgya gcig pa'i sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3240: don bzhi pas rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u bstan /
NK067(ju)001:3241: le'u bzhi bcu par bdud rtsi sman gyi sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3242: le'u so dgu par de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga /
NK067(ju)001:3244: zhe bzhi par sems dpa' sgrub cing byin dbab pa rnams bstan te /
NK067(ju)001:3245: rang gi 'dod 'bras mthar thug gi don gtso che
NK067(ju)001:3246: ba'i dbang du byas nas mchog gi dngos grub ces
NK067(ju)001:3251: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK067(ju)001:3252: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK067(ju)001:3256: dus gsum rgyal bas thugs chud pa'o //
NK067(ju)001:3257: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK067(ju)001:3258: zad pa'i dus med yid bzhin mdzod //
NK067(ju)001:3260: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK067(ju)001:3263: ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul la ni /
NK067(ju)001:3264: zhi khro'i cho ga gzhung la sogs pas mtshon bye
NK067(ju)001:3265: brag so so'i sgrub thabs gud du phyung ba rnams
NK067(ju)001:3266: dang / gtso bor ston pa ni tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa ste /
NK067(ju)001:3267: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK067(ju)001:3268: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i gzhung bsrang ba /
NK067(ju)001:3269: 'bras bu rig 'dzin sgrub pa'i dus bshad pa dang gsum gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)001:3270: brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)001:3273: gang dang gang du gsal ba'i yid //
NK067(ju)001:3274: ma yengs pa nyid ting 'dzin te //
NK067(ju)001:3276: bsgom bya'i don khyad par can bskyed rdzogs kyi ting
NK067(ju)001:3277: nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i sems rtse
NK067(ju)001:3279: sa ma d+h+ai'i sgra las drangs na mnyam pa'i blo ste /
NK067(ju)001:3282: gang bsgom bya'i don la sems rtse gcig tu zin pa'i don gyis na ting nge 'dzin no //
NK067(ju)001:3285: lha yi rnam pa'i sbyor ba yi //
NK067(ju)001:3286: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK067(ju)001:3287: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad //
NK067(ju)001:3288: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK067(ju)001:3289: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes sbyar brjod //
NK067(ju)001:3290: ces pas kun btags bskyed rim gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK067(ju)001:3291: yongs grub rdzogs rim gyi rnal 'byor gnyis las /
NK067(ju)001:3294: bskyed rim la brten skye gnas te //
NK067(ju)001:3295: mngal skyes la sogs dbye ba yis //
NK067(ju)001:3296: de yang rnam pa bzhi ru 'dod //
NK067(ju)001:3297: ces pas skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun te sgom tshul bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)001:3299: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK067(ju)001:3300: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK067(ju)001:3301: spros bcas spros dang spros med pa //
NK067(ju)001:3302: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)001:3303: zhes pas rgyas pa sgong skyes /
NK067(ju)001:3306: shin tu bsdus pa bardzusa skyes te /
NK067(ju)001:3307: de ltar skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong phyir //
NK067(ju)001:3308: spros pa rgyas pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bdag
NK067(ju)001:3309: sras gzhan sras gnyis kyi sgo nas sgom pa dang
NK067(ju)001:3310: / gzhan yang mngon byang lnga bskyed dang //
NK067(ju)001:3311: rdo rje'i cho ga bzhi bskyed la sogs pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3314: thugs phyag mtshan te cho ga gsum gyi sgo nas bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3315: bsdus pa a nu yo ga ba'i sgom tshul ltar sa bon tsam las bskyed pa'am /
NK067(ju)001:3316: bskyed sngags brjod pa'i rkyen tsam gyis bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3317: shin tu bsdus pa a ti yo ga ba'i sgom
NK067(ju)001:3318: tshul ltar chu las nya ldang gi tshul du skad
NK067(ju)001:3319: cig dran rdzogs kyis lha'i skur bskyed pa ste sgom
NK067(ju)001:3320: tshul bzhi'am / yang na lam rim ltar srid pa
NK067(ju)001:3321: mngal skyes bardzusa skyes gnyis dang bstun te sgom tshul
NK067(ju)001:3322: gnyis su bsdus nas gsungs te /
NK067(ju)001:3324: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam 'di'i bya ba'i
NK067(ju)001:3325: gdul bya'i gtso bo ni khams drug ldan gyi mi
NK067(ju)001:3326: lus yin te / sngon sbyangs pa can min pa'i
NK067(ju)001:3327: gang zag cig lam 'dir dang por zhugs nas tshe
NK067(ju)001:3328: gcig lus gcig gis zung 'jug sgrub pa'i rten gyi
NK067(ju)001:3330: de lta bas na mi'i rten can phal cher mngal skyes bardzusa skyes gnyis su 'gyur bas sam /
NK067(ju)001:3331: yang na ched du bya ba'i gdul bya de la
NK067(ju)001:3332: rim gyis pa dang gcig car ba gnyis yod pas
NK067(ju)001:3336: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa ste thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo la brten pa dang /
NK067(ju)001:3337: grol lam zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor rim gcig car
NK067(ju)001:3338: gnyis kyis bsdus pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting
NK067(ju)001:3339: nge 'dzin no // 'o na thabs lam steng sgo la /
NK067(ju)001:3342: yab yum lhar bskyed pa la sogs pa kun brtags
NK067(ju)001:3343: kyi cha 'dres pas rdzogs rim du ci'i phyir 'gyur
NK067(ju)001:3344: snyam na / bskyed rdzogs gnyis lam phan tshun ltos
NK067(ju)001:3345: pa can yin pa'i phyir thog mar kun brtags bskyed
NK067(ju)001:3346: rim gyis rang lam gyi nyams myong gtan la 'bebs
